WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.170 --> 00:00:05.870
It's about 60.000 a month
for cutting down trees. right?

2
00:00:06.570 --> 00:00:11.240
Then there's the kidney I sold.
That was 1.2 million.

3
00:00:11.680 --> 00:00:14.870
My right eye was 300.000.

4
00:00:15.530 --> 00:00:18.129
Sold one of my nuts...

5
00:00:18.130 --> 00:00:22.630
How much was that. again?
I think... not even 100.000.

6
00:00:23.750 --> 00:00:26.190
And I still owe...

7
00:00:26.510 --> 00:00:29.010
About 38.040.000 yen.

8
00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:35.719
I heard you. Pochita.

9
00:00:35.720 --> 00:00:37.730
Let's kill this thing already.

10
00:00:40.910 --> 00:00:44.400
Devil hunting pays the best. easy.

11
00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:52.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

12
00:02:15.200 --> 00:02:19.620
CHAINSAW MAN - THE COMPILATION

13
00:02:24.390 --> 00:02:26.710
Gotta be the Tomato Devil.

14
00:02:27.040 --> 00:02:29.770
He'll revive from the seeds.
so you'll wanna burn those.

15
00:02:30.150 --> 00:02:32.209
Nice work. Denji.

16
00:02:32.210 --> 00:02:36.729
This carcass will bring in a
fair price on the black market.

17
00:02:36.730 --> 00:02:38.599
I'll pay you 400.000.

18
00:02:38.600 --> 00:02:39.499
Hey. thanks!

19
00:02:39.500 --> 00:02:42.759
After what you owe and the interest.
that leaves 170.000.

20
00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:45.879
So after the finder's fee. admin fee.

21
00:02:45.880 --> 00:02:48.230
management costs. and so on...

22
00:02:48.780 --> 00:02:50.730
Leaves me with 70.000.

23
00:02:51.160 --> 00:02:57.620
After the water bill.
and some other stuff I owe...

24
00:02:58.080 --> 00:02:59.490
Funny how that works.

25
00:02:59.850 --> 00:03:02.610
I've got 1.800 yen left.

26
00:03:03.070 --> 00:03:08.879
No food at home. and this is gonna
have to last us a month. so...

27
00:03:08.880 --> 00:03:12.970
Pochita. looks like dinner's
gonna be a slice of bread.

28
00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:22.430
Why hire a brat like that to hunt devils?

29
00:03:22.860 --> 00:03:26.479
He's paying off what he owes us.

30
00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:30.310
Well. technically. it was
his deadbeat old man's debt.

31
00:03:30.630 --> 00:03:34.570
And a kid with a pet devil
can get the job done?

32
00:03:34.950 --> 00:03:37.729
The thing about real Devil Hunters is...

33
00:03:37.730 --> 00:03:42.080
They don't pass devil carcasses
onto the yakuza.

34
00:03:42.430 --> 00:03:46.580
Besides. the best thing about Denji
is he does what he's told.

35
00:03:49.760 --> 00:03:51.510
Hey. dog!

36
00:03:52.210 --> 00:03:55.149
I'll give you 100 yen to eat this cigarette.

37
00:03:55.150 --> 00:03:56.339
For real?

38
00:03:56.340 --> 00:03:57.820
Don't mind if I do.

39
00:04:03.440 --> 00:04:05.659
We'll be in touch when there's another devil.

40
00:04:05.660 --> 00:04:08.190
Try and run. and you're pig slop.

41
00:04:22.510 --> 00:04:24.450
That'll keep us for another three days.

42
00:04:27.210 --> 00:04:29.579
The other day I heard...

43
00:04:29.580 --> 00:04:33.210
That normally. people put jam
on their bread. before eating it.

44
00:04:33.510 --> 00:04:37.330
Normal's just a dream for us. though.

45
00:04:37.770 --> 00:04:40.970
Doubt I'll pay off this debt before I die.

46
00:04:44.580 --> 00:04:48.230
Probably gonna die without
ever having a girlfriend. too.

47
00:04:48.520 --> 00:04:51.789
Not like I could invite a girl to this dump.

48
00:04:51.790 --> 00:04:53.860
No money to go on dates. either.

49
00:04:58.090 --> 00:05:00.239
If I could have one dream come true...

50
00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:02.930
I wanna score with a girl before I die.

51
00:05:07.700 --> 00:05:11.959
Bastard hung himself without
paying this month's installment first.

52
00:05:11.960 --> 00:05:15.759
Boy. you've got until tomorrow
to put 700.000 together.

53
00:05:15.760 --> 00:05:18.460
You can beg for it. whore yourself out...
I don't care. Get it done.

54
00:05:18.960 --> 00:05:22.490
Otherwise. we chop you up and sell the bits.

55
00:05:36.490 --> 00:05:38.010
A ch-chainsaw...?

56
00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:43.860
A devil.

57
00:05:45.200 --> 00:05:49.280
If you're gonna kill me. just do it.
I'm dead either way.

58
00:05:58.030 --> 00:05:59.380
It's hurt?

59
00:06:00.630 --> 00:06:02.760
You're gonna die. too?

60
00:06:07.880 --> 00:06:08.849
Bite me!

61
00:06:08.850 --> 00:06:12.480
I heard that drinking blood heals a devil.

62
00:06:12.990 --> 00:06:14.840
If you don't wanna die. bite me!

63
00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:24.950
My blood's not free. though. This is a deal!

64
00:06:25.450 --> 00:06:27.200
I'll help you...

65
00:06:27.830 --> 00:06:29.240
So. you help me.

66
00:06:32.120 --> 00:06:35.450
Because I don't wanna die. after all.

67
00:06:44.740 --> 00:06:48.910
Why don't you hire me as a Devil Hunter?

68
00:06:55.140 --> 00:06:57.350
Too hungry to sleep.

69
00:06:57.660 --> 00:07:00.009
When I can't sleep.
I start thinking about money.

70
00:07:00.010 --> 00:07:01.820
and then it's even harder to sleep.

71
00:07:04.230 --> 00:07:07.490
I know what dream I wanna have when I sleep.

72
00:07:07.900 --> 00:07:11.539
Gonna put jam on my bread.
and share it with you.

73
00:07:11.540 --> 00:07:14.099
Then I'm gonna flirt with a girl...

74
00:07:14.100 --> 00:07:17.750
I'll play video games with her. and then
we'll fall asleep hugging each other.

75
00:07:18.990 --> 00:07:20.000
Sounds sweet. right?

76
00:07:34.830 --> 00:07:40.150
Y'know. I heard my mom died from some
heart disease that made her cough up blood.

77
00:07:43.130 --> 00:07:46.850
Got a devil for you. Denji. Time for work.

78
00:07:51.500 --> 00:07:55.690
Wish they'd at least let me dream...

79
00:08:04.180 --> 00:08:06.650
There's a devil in here. huh?

80
00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:11.410
You think it's hiding?

81
00:08:15.700 --> 00:08:20.689
Denji. my boy... we're pretty
grateful to you. y'know?

82
00:08:20.690 --> 00:08:22.679
Yeah?

83
00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:24.939
You're as loyal as a dog.

84
00:08:24.940 --> 00:08:28.870
and you work for cheap like one. too.

85
00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:34.130
Only problem with dogs
is I can't stand the stench.

86
00:08:41.790 --> 00:08:47.930
Even yakuza think about getting bigger
and making more money. kid.

87
00:08:48.300 --> 00:08:52.540
So we did like you.
and made a deal with a devil.

88
00:08:54.350 --> 00:08:58.230
We wanted demonic power...

89
00:08:58.550 --> 00:09:01.979
And I want Devil Hunter...

90
00:09:01.980 --> 00:09:03.480
Dead!

91
00:09:04.610 --> 00:09:09.459
Y'know. little Devil Hunter.
these guys are dumb as hell.

92
00:09:09.460 --> 00:09:11.019
Total suckers!

93
00:09:11.020 --> 00:09:17.659
I offer them a bit of demonic power.
and they offer to become my slaves...

94
00:09:17.660 --> 00:09:21.039
Even though the power
turns them into zombies.

95
00:09:21.040 --> 00:09:23.670
See. because I'm the Zombie Devil.

96
00:09:24.790 --> 00:09:28.419
And I hate Devil Hunters. because
you go around killing us devils.

97
00:09:28.420 --> 00:09:30.970
So I'm gonna kill you.

98
00:09:31.340 --> 00:09:36.680
Boys. tear him apart
and toss him in the trash.

99
00:09:37.290 --> 00:09:38.390
Shit!

100
00:09:48.780 --> 00:09:52.510
All I want is a normal life!

101
00:09:56.900 --> 00:09:59.740
And I can't even have that?!

102
00:10:18.740 --> 00:10:19.710
Pochita...

103
00:10:20.160 --> 00:10:21.180
Pochita!

104
00:10:22.310 --> 00:10:24.850
Pochita. time for work.

105
00:10:34.480 --> 00:10:39.510
Pochita. there's a good chance
I'm gonna die fighting a devil.

106
00:10:40.230 --> 00:10:43.260
My only regret would be
leaving you on your own.

107
00:10:43.710 --> 00:10:46.580
You could end up starving to death...

108
00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:50.340
Or some other Devil Hunter might kill you.

109
00:10:55.060 --> 00:10:58.960
I've heard some devils
can take over dead bodies.

110
00:11:00.110 --> 00:11:05.760
If that's something you can do...
then I want you to have my body.

111
00:11:06.780 --> 00:11:10.730
The yakuza won't be on your case
if you wait until I've been buried. right?

112
00:11:11.420 --> 00:11:15.680
And then you could move
out of here... and then...

113
00:11:16.840 --> 00:11:17.740
Yeah.

114
00:11:18.350 --> 00:11:22.510
I want you to live a normal life.
and die a normal death.

115
00:11:26.660 --> 00:11:28.730
You've gotta make my dream come true.

116
00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:54.230
Pochita?

117
00:11:57.070 --> 00:11:59.990
Did you take my body. like I said?

118
00:12:02.160 --> 00:12:06.730
I always loved hearing you talk
about your dreams. Denji.

119
00:12:08.420 --> 00:12:12.380
Here's the deal. I'll give you my heart...

120
00:12:12.690 --> 00:12:17.129
And in exchange. I want you
to show me your dream.

121
00:12:17.130 --> 00:12:18.270
Pochita?!

122
00:12:23.680 --> 00:12:24.870
I'm not hurt?

123
00:12:30.730 --> 00:12:32.150
Pochita...?

124
00:12:35.870 --> 00:12:37.400
What is this?

125
00:12:37.840 --> 00:12:40.019
You're alive after being sliced up?

126
00:12:40.020 --> 00:12:41.909
Why? Gross!

127
00:12:41.910 --> 00:12:44.909
I seriously hate Devil Hunters.

128
00:12:44.910 --> 00:12:48.330
Guys. go ahead and eat him.

129
00:12:53.110 --> 00:12:58.220
These guys had plenty already.
so why'd they want even more?

130
00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:00.590
Am I the same?

131
00:13:01.460 --> 00:13:04.350
I wasn't satisfied with
the happiness I had with Pochita.

132
00:13:04.940 --> 00:13:07.850
I kept dreaming about a better life.

133
00:13:08.560 --> 00:13:12.480
I guess we all dream
about stuff like that. huh?

134
00:13:13.300 --> 00:13:16.010
I can't blame you. then.

135
00:13:16.380 --> 00:13:18.860
And I won't. but...

136
00:13:19.910 --> 00:13:22.570
If you get in our way?

137
00:13:23.200 --> 00:13:24.510
You'll die!

138
00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:30.830
He's bound to stay dead after being eaten.

139
00:13:39.900 --> 00:13:41.909
What are you?!

140
00:13:41.910 --> 00:13:45.470
Did that devil runt take your body?!

141
00:13:45.930 --> 00:13:47.470
That means you're one of us!

142
00:14:03.660 --> 00:14:05.990
Stay away!

143
00:14:08.250 --> 00:14:09.400
Move!

144
00:14:09.900 --> 00:14:11.370
Stay back! Back! Get away!

145
00:14:11.950 --> 00:14:13.579
Stay away! Don't do it!

146
00:14:13.580 --> 00:14:15.760
Don't come near me!

147
00:14:21.170 --> 00:14:23.260
Die!

148
00:14:50.250 --> 00:14:55.710
I guess you guys went full devil. huh?

149
00:14:56.100 --> 00:14:59.469
Well. you hired me to be a Devil Hunter.

150
00:14:59.470 --> 00:15:03.590
So. I better kill all the devils. right?!

151
00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:06.009
Oh. yeah!

152
00:15:06.010 --> 00:15:08.969
Once you're all dead...

153
00:15:08.970 --> 00:15:11.360
I won't owe a damn thing!

154
00:15:21.430 --> 00:15:23.490
Someone got here before us.

155
00:15:24.650 --> 00:15:26.490
There's still one alive.

156
00:15:38.030 --> 00:15:41.110
You've got a strange smell.

157
00:15:41.850 --> 00:15:44.440
Not like a human or a devil.

158
00:15:47.260 --> 00:15:49.260
I take it you did this?

159
00:15:52.360 --> 00:15:55.680
H-Hug me...

160
00:16:10.150 --> 00:16:11.369
He's human.

161
00:16:11.370 --> 00:16:13.909
Any chance he's possessed?

162
00:16:13.910 --> 00:16:15.499
No.

163
00:16:15.500 --> 00:16:17.890
I can tell who's possessed
with a look at their face.

164
00:16:20.340 --> 00:16:23.419
I came here to kill the Zombie Devil.

165
00:16:23.420 --> 00:16:25.750
I'm a Devil Hunter with Public Safety.

166
00:16:28.480 --> 00:16:30.830
You have two options:

167
00:16:31.220 --> 00:16:34.490
I can kill you like a devil.

168
00:16:34.980 --> 00:16:37.650
or I can keep you as a human.

169
00:16:38.560 --> 00:16:41.600
If I keep you. I'll make sure you're fed.

170
00:16:48.980 --> 00:16:50.600
When you say that...

171
00:16:51.590 --> 00:16:53.620
Like. what's for breakfast?

172
00:16:55.830 --> 00:17:01.039
Bread with butter and jam. salad. coffee...

173
00:17:01.040 --> 00:17:05.130
And then maybe something
for dessert. I think?

174
00:17:09.030 --> 00:17:11.890
That sounds awesome.

175
00:17:12.840 --> 00:17:15.890
CHAINSAW MAN - THE COMPILATION

176
00:17:22.430 --> 00:17:24.150
That was my stomach.

177
00:17:25.430 --> 00:17:27.650
What's your name?

178
00:17:28.630 --> 00:17:29.670
It's Denji!

179
00:17:30.030 --> 00:17:32.160
We haven't had breakfast yet. either.

180
00:17:32.990 --> 00:17:35.420
Let's grab something at the rest area.

181
00:17:36.440 --> 00:17:39.409
Sorry. but I don't have any cash.

182
00:17:39.410 --> 00:17:43.050
Just pick what you want. I'll pay.

183
00:17:44.420 --> 00:17:47.250
And you're conspicuous
without a shirt on. so wear this.

184
00:17:48.240 --> 00:17:49.240
Here.

185
00:17:54.120 --> 00:17:58.339
All my life people have avoided me.
saying I'm filthy and smell bad.

186
00:17:58.340 --> 00:18:00.390
No one's ever been nice to me before.

187
00:18:00.770 --> 00:18:03.440
Much less a girl who looks this good!

188
00:18:06.020 --> 00:18:07.450
I love her!

189
00:18:10.430 --> 00:18:12.029
I'll take some udon...

190
00:18:12.030 --> 00:18:13.300
(Sausage. Corn Dog. Curry Udon. Curry Rice. Udon • Soba. Ramen)
Udon and... a sausage!

191
00:18:13.301 --> 00:18:14.779
Udon and... a sausage!

192
00:18:14.780 --> 00:18:15.829
Is that cool?

193
00:18:15.830 --> 00:18:19.129
Sure is. I'll take a curry udon. please.

194
00:18:19.130 --> 00:18:20.159
Coming up.

195
00:18:20.160 --> 00:18:23.579
Oh. that sounds good. too...

196
00:18:23.580 --> 00:18:24.730
Whoa. there.

197
00:18:25.720 --> 00:18:27.229
You smell good.

198
00:18:27.230 --> 00:18:29.050
You okay?

199
00:18:29.670 --> 00:18:31.040
- It'll be 1.100 yen. all together.
- Sorry about that!

200
00:18:31.460 --> 00:18:34.180
The chainsaws cut me up. too.

201
00:18:34.550 --> 00:18:36.949
- Here's 2.000.
- so I think I'm a little low on blood right now.

202
00:18:37.430 --> 00:18:40.310
How did you end up like this?

203
00:18:40.620 --> 00:18:43.950
I had a pet devil. and he replaced my heart.

204
00:18:44.860 --> 00:18:46.689
Kinda hard to believe. huh?

205
00:18:46.690 --> 00:18:49.139
I don't really wanna believe it. either.

206
00:18:49.140 --> 00:18:52.280
Pochita dying for my sake...

207
00:18:56.580 --> 00:18:59.419
There's not a lot of precedent
for your condition.

208
00:18:59.420 --> 00:19:01.450
even from a historical perspective.

209
00:19:02.090 --> 00:19:04.810
It doesn't even have a name.

210
00:19:06.640 --> 00:19:09.090
I believe you.

211
00:19:10.280 --> 00:19:13.340
I've got a particularly good sense of smell.

212
00:19:13.740 --> 00:19:15.220
So I can tell.

213
00:19:15.640 --> 00:19:18.799
Your best friend is alive inside of you.

214
00:19:18.800 --> 00:19:21.279
Not in the sentimental sense. either.

215
00:19:21.280 --> 00:19:25.440
Your body has the scents
of both a human and a devil.

216
00:19:26.160 --> 00:19:27.359
Is that right?

217
00:19:27.360 --> 00:19:28.519
That's awesome!

218
00:19:28.520 --> 00:19:31.270
Really... awesome...

219
00:19:38.450 --> 00:19:39.590
Udon?!

220
00:19:41.310 --> 00:19:42.190
The udon?

221
00:19:48.570 --> 00:19:50.840
Is it cool if I eat my udon?

222
00:19:52.220 --> 00:19:55.089
Are you all right?
Can you eat on your own?

223
00:19:55.090 --> 00:19:56.200
I can...

224
00:19:57.700 --> 00:19:59.040
I can not.

225
00:19:59.340 --> 00:20:01.459
Here. Say. "Ahh."

226
00:20:01.460 --> 00:20:03.350
Ahh...

227
00:20:04.380 --> 00:20:05.219
Is it good?

228
00:20:05.220 --> 00:20:06.229
Woof!

229
00:20:06.230 --> 00:20:11.479
You are really sweet to be
enjoying soggy udon this much.

230
00:20:11.480 --> 00:20:13.320
A lot like a dog. actually.

231
00:20:16.650 --> 00:20:19.360
Um... what's your name?

232
00:20:20.660 --> 00:20:21.740
Makima.

233
00:20:22.030 --> 00:20:26.760
Miss Makima... is there
a type of guy you l-like?

234
00:20:33.430 --> 00:20:35.920
I'm into the "Denji" type.

235
00:20:36.740 --> 00:20:37.650
Denji?

236
00:20:41.030 --> 00:20:42.140
Dude. that's me.

237
00:20:46.810 --> 00:20:49.230
Denji? This way. come on.

238
00:20:51.230 --> 00:20:54.270
(Tokyo Devil Hunters Headquarters)
This is the Tokyo headquarters
for our Devil Hunters.

239
00:20:56.260 --> 00:21:01.499
There are over a thousand Devil Hunters
in Tokyo. including civilians.

240
00:21:01.500 --> 00:21:06.060
but Public Safety has the best benefits
and a lot of paid vacation time.

241
00:21:09.220 --> 00:21:12.130
If Miss Makima likes me...

242
00:21:12.400 --> 00:21:16.590
Then maybe. if we work together.
we'll eventually get together?

243
00:21:17.130 --> 00:21:21.410
And if we get together...
we can get together. right?

244
00:21:21.880 --> 00:21:25.140
I wanna! I wanna get together
with her real bad!

245
00:21:27.990 --> 00:21:29.269
Denji...

246
00:21:29.270 --> 00:21:30.520
Yeah?

247
00:21:31.140 --> 00:21:34.020
We're supposed to wear uniforms.
so put this on.

248
00:21:34.440 --> 00:21:37.090
Once you've changed.
I'll introduce you to a coworker.

249
00:21:44.320 --> 00:21:49.580
This is Aki Hayakawa. He started
three years before you. Denji.

250
00:21:49.960 --> 00:21:52.380
You're going to be shadowing him today.

251
00:21:53.370 --> 00:21:56.449
I'm not working with you. Miss Makima?

252
00:21:56.450 --> 00:21:58.089
That should be obvious.

253
00:21:58.090 --> 00:22:00.909
You're not even in her league.

254
00:22:00.910 --> 00:22:02.059
Time for patrol.

255
00:22:02.060 --> 00:22:04.840
No! Miss Makima!

256
00:22:05.660 --> 00:22:07.259
Damn it. get up.

257
00:22:07.260 --> 00:22:10.750
No way! I wanna work with Miss Makima!

258
00:22:13.210 --> 00:22:17.710
If you do a good job.
