00:38:20.900 --> 00:38:26.059
Before I was able to recover Meowy.
I fell into Makima's clutches.

509
00:38:26.060 --> 00:38:30.210
My dear Meowy may be dead already.
and yet... I find it hard to give up hope.

510
00:38:30.800 --> 00:38:33.619
If it lets me retrieve Meowy from that demon.

511
00:38:33.620 --> 00:38:36.230
I'm willing to abide humans.
or anything else I needs must.

512
00:38:36.790 --> 00:38:40.550
I doubt you'd understand
such concern for a cat.

513
00:38:40.830 --> 00:38:44.220
For a cat? That's dumb as hell.

514
00:38:44.620 --> 00:38:48.190
But I'd do whatever it takes
to get to fondle some boobs.

515
00:38:49.750 --> 00:38:52.830
It seems I may never understand humans.

516
00:38:55.990 --> 00:38:58.820
But I think I'd get you if it was a dog.

517
00:39:01.150 --> 00:39:04.009
What would you say to the
prospect of fondling my chest

518
00:39:04.010 --> 00:39:06.110
after retrieving Meowy from that devil?

519
00:39:10.430 --> 00:39:12.080
That fucking devil...

520
00:39:12.870 --> 00:39:16.120
thinks he can just kidnap some poor cat?!

521
00:39:17.130 --> 00:39:19.710
Well. I don't think so!

522
00:39:21.870 --> 00:39:23.800
As a Devil Hunter. I say no!

523
00:39:24.800 --> 00:39:28.860
I'm gonna kill the shit out of that devil!

524
00:39:30.630 --> 00:39:33.630
Leave for the Fiend. Power. is approved.

525
00:39:35.150 --> 00:39:37.520
Make sure to have her back by 5:00 PM.

526
00:39:37.990 --> 00:39:40.579
You're not even allowed to go out on your own?

527
00:39:40.580 --> 00:39:44.150
Indeed. I've had to idly
while away my time in here.

528
00:39:49.130 --> 00:39:52.509
I know where the devil
that kidnapped Meowy dwells.

529
00:39:52.510 --> 00:39:55.290
The concern is that you are
the only one who can fight it.

530
00:39:56.630 --> 00:40:01.380
He's likely to use Meowy
as a shield upon seeing me.

531
00:40:02.060 --> 00:40:04.330
If that happens. then all is lost.

532
00:40:07.180 --> 00:40:10.280
I had a pet devil named Pochita. y'know?

533
00:40:10.710 --> 00:40:14.330
I can't pet him anymore. but it's cool.

534
00:40:15.270 --> 00:40:17.490
Because he's alive in here.

535
00:40:17.830 --> 00:40:20.000
How foolish you humans are.

536
00:40:20.810 --> 00:40:23.999
Does that not mean Pochita is dead?

537
00:40:24.000 --> 00:40:28.070
Death is the absence of life.
This nonsense about living on in your heart

538
00:40:28.340 --> 00:40:30.400
is little more than miserable self-comfort.

539
00:40:35.900 --> 00:40:38.870
Uh-huh. I guess so.

540
00:40:40.490 --> 00:40:45.280
I don't think I'm ever
gonna get along with her.

541
00:40:50.580 --> 00:40:55.809
The American matter has got the Soviet
war hawks crowing more loudly than ever.

542
00:40:55.810 --> 00:40:59.939
There are rumors about
the military use of devils. as well.

543
00:40:59.940 --> 00:41:05.279
Hopefully. devils will remain
Japan's only enemies in the future.

544
00:41:05.280 --> 00:41:07.499
Makima. how are the hunting dogs

545
00:41:07.500 --> 00:41:09.699
that have been added
to the squad performing?

546
00:41:09.700 --> 00:41:14.870
There's one that seems promising.
and another that seems interesting.

547
00:41:15.220 --> 00:41:16.699
Interesting...?

548
00:41:16.700 --> 00:41:18.870
A pup that I just recently picked up.

549
00:41:20.280 --> 00:41:24.729
Your job is to raise these hounds.
and then put them to work.

550
00:41:24.730 --> 00:41:27.910
Make sure not to grow attached.

551
00:41:35.350 --> 00:41:38.470
As far as I can tell.
Denji's disgusting. not "interesting."

552
00:41:39.230 --> 00:41:41.600
Why do you have such high hopes for him?

553
00:41:47.020 --> 00:41:50.820
All devils are born with names.

554
00:41:51.120 --> 00:41:54.159
And the more those names are feared.

555
00:41:54.160 --> 00:41:56.750
the more powerful the devil is said to become.

556
00:41:57.330 --> 00:42:01.929
Coffee isn't considered very frightening.

557
00:42:01.930 --> 00:42:05.020
so a Coffee Devil would probably be weak.

558
00:42:05.790 --> 00:42:09.270
But what about a Car Devil?

559
00:42:09.640 --> 00:42:13.970
It's easy to imagine being run over and dying.
so it would probably be strong.

560
00:42:15.580 --> 00:42:19.100
And Denji can turn into a Chainsaw Devil.

561
00:42:20.820 --> 00:42:23.110
Seems pretty interesting to me.

562
00:42:26.770 --> 00:42:30.280
He might be interesting.
but I'm not sure he'll be any use.

563
00:42:31.050 --> 00:42:35.229
Everyone in Public Safety has
a real goal or motivation.

564
00:42:35.230 --> 00:42:39.540
But he said he just wants
to live the good life.

565
00:42:40.000 --> 00:42:42.509
He's a bad fit for our operation.

566
00:42:42.510 --> 00:42:46.030
Not only that. but he thinks
he can be friends with devils.

567
00:42:46.980 --> 00:42:50.130
He's still a kid. A stupid brat.

568
00:42:50.510 --> 00:42:52.439
That is the house!

569
00:42:52.440 --> 00:42:54.890
Meowy and the devil are in there.

570
00:42:57.460 --> 00:42:59.370
Well. we better get going. then.

571
00:43:05.080 --> 00:43:06.670
What is it now?

572
00:43:07.040 --> 00:43:10.720
Isn't he gonna use the cat
as a hostage if he sees you?

573
00:43:11.210 --> 00:43:13.569
Should you even. like. be this close?

574
00:43:13.570 --> 00:43:17.069
Oh. I did say that. didn't I?

575
00:43:17.070 --> 00:43:18.449
You said...?

576
00:43:18.450 --> 00:43:21.200
I misspoke.

577
00:43:29.280 --> 00:43:33.730
Fool that you are. it seems
your instincts are sharp.

578
00:43:37.090 --> 00:43:41.709
You kept me waiting
a long time. Blood Devil.

579
00:43:41.710 --> 00:43:44.230
I thought you had run away.

580
00:43:45.560 --> 00:43:49.680
Spare me your complaints!
It took me this long to gain some freedom.

581
00:43:50.140 --> 00:43:53.640
And I've brought a human
just as you demanded. Bat!

582
00:43:54.950 --> 00:43:57.759
My first meal in ages...

583
00:43:57.760 --> 00:44:02.710
A young man? I'm sure his
blood will be full of vigor.

584
00:44:08.440 --> 00:44:11.559
Look at my arm. human.

585
00:44:11.560 --> 00:44:14.549
The wound that your kind gave me!

586
00:44:14.550 --> 00:44:20.010
The damnable wound
that forced me into hiding!

587
00:44:20.780 --> 00:44:22.679
Like I give a shit. Dumbass.

588
00:44:22.680 --> 00:44:24.829
Food shouldn't speak!

589
00:44:24.830 --> 00:44:30.740
Time to heal the wounds humans
gave me with human blood!

590
00:44:36.900 --> 00:44:38.150
Disgusting!

591
00:44:39.400 --> 00:44:45.210
I've been revived with awful-tasting blood!

592
00:44:49.170 --> 00:44:52.059
The inside of my mouth tastes disgusting...

593
00:44:52.060 --> 00:44:55.670
I need to cleanse my palate
with another human now!

594
00:45:02.800 --> 00:45:05.810
What are you trying to do?
Make friends with them?

595
00:45:08.600 --> 00:45:12.610
I'm amazed you actually believed my story.

596
00:45:14.730 --> 00:45:17.710
Humans truly are foolish.

597
00:45:19.190 --> 00:45:21.360
The stench of cigarettes...

598
00:45:21.640 --> 00:45:24.619
The scent of makeup and drugs...

599
00:45:24.620 --> 00:45:25.459
Are you serious?

600
00:45:25.460 --> 00:45:26.570
Wow!

601
00:45:27.670 --> 00:45:30.370
There's a decent aroma.

602
00:45:30.730 --> 00:45:33.839
I'll cleanse my palate with some children.

603
00:45:33.840 --> 00:45:35.250
Bat Devil!

604
00:45:36.790 --> 00:45:39.470
I brought you a human. as promised!

605
00:45:39.760 --> 00:45:41.720
Release Meowy.

606
00:45:44.330 --> 00:45:48.480
Oh. I did say I'd do that. didn't I?

607
00:45:52.100 --> 00:45:53.229
Meowy!

608
00:45:53.230 --> 00:45:58.610
But I hadn't punished you for bringing me
such nasty blood yet. had I?

609
00:46:03.050 --> 00:46:04.200
Meowy...?

610
00:46:04.640 --> 00:46:05.949
Meowy!

611
00:46:05.950 --> 00:46:08.139
Your name shall be Meowy!

612
00:46:08.140 --> 00:46:11.200
You smell tasty. for a cat.

613
00:46:15.210 --> 00:46:17.980
So spindly. though.

614
00:46:18.910 --> 00:46:22.060
Let's put some meat
on those bones before I feast.

615
00:46:28.710 --> 00:46:30.760
Grow big and strong. now.

616
00:46:31.100 --> 00:46:34.450
I'm looking forward to killing you. Meowy.

617
00:46:42.790 --> 00:46:46.620
I've killed all who've met my eyes.

618
00:46:47.820 --> 00:46:51.990
It's become strange to hear a voice
that isn't screaming.

619
00:46:53.320 --> 00:46:54.980
So strange...

620
00:46:58.860 --> 00:47:01.210
Blood Devil...

621
00:47:01.710 --> 00:47:04.090
I need blood.

622
00:47:04.580 --> 00:47:10.730
If you want to save this cat.
then bring me a human.

623
00:47:23.720 --> 00:47:26.790
You said you couldn't pet Pochita anymore. yes?

624
00:47:28.140 --> 00:47:30.450
I understand how you feel now.

625
00:47:31.340 --> 00:47:33.150
'Tis an awful feeling.

626
00:47:40.140 --> 00:47:41.709
Nasty!

627
00:47:41.710 --> 00:47:44.110
All of this repulsive blood!

628
00:47:47.890 --> 00:47:50.640
The inside of my mouth feels filthy!

629
00:47:50.990 --> 00:47:53.890
I need to gargle with the blood of children!

630
00:47:58.650 --> 00:48:03.149
After I gargle. a virgin
should make a fine appetizer.

631
00:48:03.150 --> 00:48:06.469
Then a beefy man for a main course...

632
00:48:06.470 --> 00:48:09.350
And a pregnant woman for dessert.

633
00:48:12.640 --> 00:48:15.459
Gimme my tits back!

634
00:48:15.460 --> 00:48:19.329
You're drinking my blood?!
That's disgusting!

635
00:48:19.330 --> 00:48:23.000
I don't even feel like drinking your blood!

636
00:48:24.980 --> 00:48:27.290
There was a time I couldn't find Pochita.

637
00:48:28.120 --> 00:48:30.510
He was gone when I woke up in the morning...

638
00:48:31.110 --> 00:48:33.420
So I looked all over town.
but couldn't find him.

639
00:48:34.720 --> 00:48:37.390
I thought a devil might've eaten him.

640
00:48:38.720 --> 00:48:43.150
but when I got home.
he was crying. waiting for me.

641
00:48:43.850 --> 00:48:46.790
I remember being so relieved.
I fell asleep holding him.

642
00:48:48.140 --> 00:48:54.120
I wonder how she felt when she tried to sleep.
knowing that devil had Meowy.

643
00:49:05.000 --> 00:49:07.950
You're a devil?!

644
00:49:14.040 --> 00:49:16.590
Hey. dumbass! You wanna get eaten?!

645
00:49:19.190 --> 00:49:21.770
You let her escape?

646
00:49:22.180 --> 00:49:26.030
You're a devil!
What do you think you're doing?!

647
00:49:27.620 --> 00:49:29.739
Think I'm gonna split open your guts...

648
00:49:29.740 --> 00:49:32.740
And then cop me a feel!

649
00:50:06.170 --> 00:50:09.280
If you're so set on saving humans...

650
00:50:11.900 --> 00:50:14.200
Can you cut through this?!

651
00:50:17.910 --> 00:50:19.699
The chainsaws retract?!

652
00:50:19.700 --> 00:50:22.139
Such brute strength in that tiny body!

653
00:50:22.140 --> 00:50:25.280
Why would you use that power
to save a human?!

654
00:50:27.080 --> 00:50:29.460
You think I saved him?

655
00:50:30.210 --> 00:50:34.339
(Western Tokyo)
I don't give a shit...

656
00:50:34.340 --> 00:50:36.010
about saving some dude!

657
00:51:06.220 --> 00:51:08.239
I need to heal now.

658
00:51:08.240 --> 00:51:11.340
Your blood reeks of cigarettes.
but it should do. for now.

659
00:51:14.340 --> 00:51:17.640
How are you still alive?!

660
00:51:19.350 --> 00:51:22.990
Through all of this crap...

661
00:51:24.300 --> 00:51:26.900
I've been about as patient as possible.

662
00:51:28.400 --> 00:51:31.539
So how come I haven't...

663
00:51:31.540 --> 00:51:37.200
gotten to cop a single damn feel yet?!

664
00:51:41.420 --> 00:51:44.410
S-Stay away!

665
00:52:14.320 --> 00:52:17.410
CHAINSAW MAN - THE COMPILATION

666
00:52:35.510 --> 00:52:41.510
If you want to save this cat.
then bring me a human.

667
00:52:45.860 --> 00:52:48.140
One life is worth as little as any other.

668
00:52:48.790 --> 00:52:50.390
And this is only a cat.

669
00:52:51.150 --> 00:52:54.650
So why do I run?
Why do I search for a human?

670
00:52:58.080 --> 00:53:00.030
Is it to save Meowy?

671
00:53:04.450 --> 00:53:06.750
Such a foolish reason.

672
00:53:11.120 --> 00:53:12.800
I love blood.

673
00:53:13.240 --> 00:53:17.130
The taste. the smell.
the sense of mortality...

674
00:53:18.270 --> 00:53:22.780
And then... there is something
I only recently realized:

675
00:53:24.030 --> 00:53:25.970
The blood is warm...

676
00:53:27.100 --> 00:53:28.980
And feels pleasant.

677
00:53:41.640 --> 00:53:43.890
Why did you save me?

678
00:53:44.780 --> 00:53:47.120
I attempted to kill you.

679
00:53:59.040 --> 00:54:01.350
Such a foolish reason.

680
00:54:09.000 --> 00:54:11.050
Forgive my deceit.

681
00:54:11.480 --> 00:54:13.980
Since Meowy is safe...

682
00:54:14.580 --> 00:54:16.560
You may fondle my chest.

683
00:54:25.450 --> 00:54:31.000
Hell yeah!

684
00:54:33.500 --> 00:54:37.250
Holy shit! Ow!

685
00:54:38.170 --> 00:54:39.510
That hurts!

686
00:54:58.110 --> 00:54:59.340
Can you move?

687
00:54:59.900 --> 00:55:01.740
Not even a finger.

688
00:55:02.140 --> 00:55:04.240
Take Meowy and flee. please.

689
00:55:13.330 --> 00:55:15.960
Damn it. not enough chainsaw...

690
00:55:17.660 --> 00:55:19.490
I must be low on blood.

691
00:55:22.830 --> 00:55:25.720
And after I finally found him...

692
00:55:26.260 --> 00:55:29.889
It's you. right? The one who killed Batty.

693
00:55:29.890 --> 00:55:32.520
He was my man. y'know?!

694
00:55:34.020 --> 00:55:38.330
Oh... but you're actually pretty cute yourself.

695
00:55:38.770 --> 00:55:42.400
You're my type. so I'll let you go!

696
00:55:43.390 --> 00:55:44.900
What about them?

697
00:55:48.010 --> 00:55:49.530
They die.

698
00:55:54.800 --> 00:55:57.130
Then you can die. too.

699
00:56:29.450 --> 00:56:31.900
He can fight so fiercely...

700
00:56:32.720 --> 00:56:34.700
To merely fondle a chest?

701
00:56:48.540 --> 00:56:50.259
Is this a joke?

702
00:56:50.260 --> 00:56:54.270
How'd a little pupper like you kill my Batty?

703
00:56:56.770 --> 00:57:02.020
Y'know. he and I shared a dream:
killing and eating all of humanity.

704
00:57:02.440 --> 00:57:05.779
A pipe dream. but a noble one.
and a romantic one.

705
00:57:05.780 --> 00:57:09.549
And now this little yipping dog has ruined it.

706
00:57:09.550 --> 00:57:12.410
You're cute enough that I regret it...

707
00:57:13.120 --> 00:57:14.790
But you still need to die.

708
00:57:16.700 --> 00:57:19.039
I'm not dying before I cop a feel.

709
00:57:19.040 --> 00:57:20.839
That is ridiculous!

710
00:57:20.840 --> 00:57:24.479
To think he was killed by someone
with such a trashy dream.

711
00:57:24.480 --> 00:57:27.300
Alas. poor Batty...

712
00:57:28.550 --> 00:57:30.590
Such a foolish reason.

713
00:57:31.840 --> 00:57:33.760
Everyone is serious about this except you.

714
00:57:54.640 --> 00:57:59.329
Everybody wants to trash-talk my plans...

715
00:57:59.330 --> 00:58:00.659
It's revenge this.

716
00:58:00.660 --> 00:58:02.329
protect my family that.

717
00:58:02.330 --> 00:58:03.829
and save a cat. too!

718
00:58:03.830 --> 00:58:05.819
Blah. blah. blah!

719
00:58:05.820 --> 00:58:08.839
I guess your fancy dreams
make you guys hot shit. huh?!

720
00:58:08.840 --> 00:58:11.709
How about we have us a dream battle. then?!
How about that?!

721
00:58:11.710 --> 00:58:14.599
If I murderize you.

722
00:58:14.600 --> 00:58:18.219
that means your dream's
weaker than fondling a tit!

723
00:58:18.220 --> 00:58:20.079
Even your howls are cute!

724
00:58:20.080 --> 00:58:22.459
But y'know what they say about
little dogs barking! Yap. yap. yap!

725
00:58:22.460 --> 00:58:25.730
Okay! I'll gobble you up. then!

726
00:58:26.690 --> 00:58:27.859
Go ahead...

727
00:58:27.860 --> 00:58:32.380
If you can beat me in the dream battle!

728
00:59:04.430 --> 00:59:05.900
Demoniacal...

729
00:59:43.730 --> 00:59:46.980
Time to eat...

730
00:59:52.810 --> 00:59:53.750
Kon.
59:59.620 --> 01:00:02.159
Huh... Huh?

731
01:00:02.160 --> 01:00:06.669
Looks like she's the Leech Devil.
May I swallow?

732
01:00:06.670 --> 01:00:07.840
Do it.

733
01:00:23.190 --> 01:00:25.430
The Leech Devil's extermination is confirmed.

734
01:00:25.770 --> 01:00:28.639
I want the rookies handling search
and rescue. plus assisting with the evac.

735
01:00:28.640 --> 01:00:29.769
- Yes. sir!
- Okay!

736
01:00:29.770 --> 01:00:33.299
Himeno. you've got seniority.
so keep watch for more devils.

737
01:00:33.300 --> 01:00:34.330
On it.

738
01:00:35.400 --> 01:00:39.529
Dream battle... Gonna... My dream battle...

739
01:00:39.530 --> 01:00:42.450
You and the Blood Fiend
need to be debriefed.

740
01:00:43.790 --> 01:00:45.340
And Meowy?

741
01:00:49.290 --> 01:00:52.539
Have the cat sent to a veterinarian
for a thorough checkup.

742
01:00:52.540 --> 01:00:55.630
CHAINSAW MAN - THE COMPILATION

743
01:01:06.110 --> 01:01:09.670
I found your arm.

744
01:01:10.600 --> 01:01:12.770
A blood infusion was all it needed to reattach.

745
01:01:13.460 --> 01:01:15.710
You really are like a devil.

746
01:01:17.000 --> 01:01:20.029
You seemed pretty friendly
with that devil back there.

747
01:01:20.030 --> 01:01:21.990
I saw.

748
01:01:23.780 --> 01:01:26.159
You really don't know a thing. huh?

749
01:01:26.160 --> 01:01:30.360
Devil Hunters form contracts with devils
in order to fight against them.

750
01:01:31.810 --> 01:01:34.489
I've got a contract with the Fox Devil.

751
01:01:34.490 --> 01:01:39.190
In exchange for power.
I offer up a bit of my body as food.

752
01:01:39.680 --> 01:01:41.590
It was some skin this time.

753
01:01:43.100 --> 01:01:44.390
Sounds painful.

754
01:01:45.310 --> 01:01:47.930
Devils yearn for the deaths of humans.

755
01:01:48.490 --> 01:01:50.640
The same goes for Fiends.

756
01:01:52.070 --> 01:01:54.270
Power seems cool. though.

757
01:01:56.890 --> 01:02:00.029
The surveillance cameras caught
you two headed to your patrol area.

758
01:02:00.030 --> 01:02:02.019
(Paused)
The surveillance cameras caught
you two headed to your patrol area.

759
01:02:02.020 --> 01:02:06.939
(Paused)
And the house that we believe
was housing the Bat Devil

760
01:02:06.940 --> 01:02:09.100
contained a lot of your spilt blood.

761
01:02:09.780 --> 01:02:13.460
The Blood Fiend tried to kill you. didn't she?

762
01:02:13.930 --> 01:02:18.710
I don't know why. but you're trying
to protect a devil. Again.

763
01:02:19.200 --> 01:02:22.450
I dunno... is that how it happened?

764
01:02:25.480 --> 01:02:29.249
My daughter would like
to meet the chainsaw guy.

765
01:02:29.250 --> 01:02:30.640
Thank you.

766
01:02:31.220 --> 01:02:35.159
The devil threatened to eat me
back at the office.

767
01:02:35.160 --> 01:02:37.729
but now that I think about it. he was
wearing a Public Safety uniform.

768
01:02:37.730 --> 01:02:39.390
I'd like to thank him.

769
01:02:39.980 --> 01:02:42.299
"Don't give a shit about
saving some dude." he says!

770
01:02:42.300 --> 01:02:44.499
And then the devil throws
my car with me in it!

771
01:02:44.500 --> 01:02:46.840
It was a devil with a chainsaw
coming out of its head...

772
01:02:50.260 --> 01:02:53.679
If I dig deeper into this.
and report it to the higher-ups.

773
01:02:53.680 --> 01:02:57.270
it'd mean the Blood Fiend gets disposed of
along with you. since you covered for her.

774
01:02:57.920 --> 01:02:59.879
But there were no fatalities.

775
