So. if you're willing to accept one condition.
I'll let what happened slide.

776
01:03:08.630 --> 01:03:11.390
You need to do what I tell you to.

777
01:03:11.860 --> 01:03:14.649
You're a dumbass and a brat
with no clue about right and wrong.

778
01:03:14.650 --> 01:03:19.050
I've been doing this longer. so I'm pretty
sure I have some grasp of social ethics.

779
01:03:19.400 --> 01:03:23.900
All you need to do to protect
this lifestyle is listen to me.

780
01:03:26.750 --> 01:03:29.410
How about it?
If you follow. I want an answer.

781
01:03:31.910 --> 01:03:34.920
Sure. I'll keep it in mind.

782
01:03:36.410 --> 01:03:38.419
You can relax.

783
01:03:38.420 --> 01:03:41.839
I might not be after some
big-deal goal like you guys.

784
01:03:41.840 --> 01:03:44.540
and I might dream small.

785
01:03:45.130 --> 01:03:49.180
But I'm as serious about this as you are.

786
01:03:49.700 --> 01:03:52.130
You can count on me.

787
01:03:56.140 --> 01:03:58.689
Try and learn some manners in the meantime.

788
01:03:58.690 --> 01:04:02.170
Yeah. I'll think about it.

789
01:04:08.460 --> 01:04:11.090
You see? Am I not innocent?

790
01:04:13.840 --> 01:04:16.919
Now. would you kindly take these off?

791
01:04:16.920 --> 01:04:19.589
Is this a good idea?

792
01:04:19.590 --> 01:04:22.809
When this cutie-Fiend kills somebody.

793
01:04:22.810 --> 01:04:25.669
it's gonna be your responsibility.
for letting her live.

794
01:04:25.670 --> 01:04:28.219
We're Devil Hunters.

795
01:04:28.220 --> 01:04:30.019
Whether they're devils or Fiends.

796
01:04:30.020 --> 01:04:32.480
if they're handy.
we should put them to work.

797
01:04:32.930 --> 01:04:36.650
But they're still the enemy.
We're just making use of them.

798
01:04:37.380 --> 01:04:39.610
We're not making friends.

799
01:04:42.940 --> 01:04:45.870
What a pitiful home this is!

800
01:04:49.200 --> 01:04:53.480
I'd like you to put Power up
in one of your rooms. Hayakawa.

801
01:04:53.830 --> 01:04:58.829
I think you'll make a good leash
for the two of them.

802
01:04:58.830 --> 01:05:02.339
- Stop right there. Meowy!
- Is there some reason why you're sending me all
these psychos. ma'am?

803
01:05:02.340 --> 01:05:04.869
- It seems you've got quite a feast!
- It's because I trust you more than anyone else.

804
01:05:04.870 --> 01:05:06.839
- Damn it. who said you could come in?!
- It's because I trust you more than anyone else.

805
01:05:06.840 --> 01:05:08.029
'Tis mine now!

806
01:05:08.030 --> 01:05:10.090
Gimme my super toast back!

807
01:05:10.620 --> 01:05:12.850
Oh... okay.

808
01:05:13.110 --> 01:05:16.230
It'd be a little odd to have her
staying at the office indefinitely.

809
01:05:19.850 --> 01:05:20.950
Okay.

810
01:05:21.990 --> 01:05:27.110
You don't need to worry.
Power said she would behave.

811
01:05:27.400 --> 01:05:28.840
It'll be fine.

812
01:05:31.110 --> 01:05:32.779
Vegetables are revolting!

813
01:05:32.780 --> 01:05:33.579
Away!

814
01:05:33.580 --> 01:05:34.789
Carrot!

815
01:05:34.790 --> 01:05:36.389
Don't fling your vegetables!

816
01:05:36.390 --> 01:05:37.469
Damn it...

817
01:05:37.470 --> 01:05:41.780
Show some respect to the farmers
who grew the veggies. devil!

818
01:05:42.380 --> 01:05:44.589
I prefer to only occasionally bathe.

819
01:05:44.590 --> 01:05:45.419
Get in there!

820
01:05:45.420 --> 01:05:46.669
You reek!

821
01:05:46.670 --> 01:05:47.709
The toilet?

822
01:05:47.710 --> 01:05:50.089
I prefer to only occasionally flush my feces.

823
01:05:50.090 --> 01:05:51.349
Flush it!

824
01:05:51.350 --> 01:05:52.549
It stinks.

825
01:05:52.550 --> 01:05:54.639
You two are absurd.

826
01:05:54.640 --> 01:05:57.219
How delicate these humans be.

827
01:05:57.220 --> 01:05:58.560
Aren't they. Meowy?

828
01:06:05.570 --> 01:06:09.069
Can't believe she just shows up
and starts raising hell.

829
01:06:09.070 --> 01:06:11.819
Do devils not flush the toilet?

830
01:06:11.820 --> 01:06:13.979
Didn't eat her veggies either.

831
01:06:13.980 --> 01:06:15.330
You there...

832
01:06:16.340 --> 01:06:21.080
Hey. Shit Devil! Your turds are stuck
to the damn toilet and won't come off!

833
01:06:27.310 --> 01:06:29.289
We had a deal. did we not?

834
01:06:29.290 --> 01:06:31.779
You may fondle my chest.

835
01:06:31.780 --> 01:06:32.860
So. fondle!

836
01:06:43.920 --> 01:06:47.029
Come now. what's the matter?
Aren't you pleased?

837
01:06:47.030 --> 01:06:48.570
Commence your fondling.

838
01:06:53.770 --> 01:06:55.570
