839
01:06:56.750 --> 01:07:00.200
You have earned three squeezes of my breast.

840
01:07:00.780 --> 01:07:02.250
Three?

841
01:07:02.960 --> 01:07:05.629
One for your rescue of Meowy.

842
01:07:05.630 --> 01:07:08.359
A second for slaying the Bat Devil.

843
01:07:08.360 --> 01:07:12.970
And a third for protecting me from topknot!

844
01:07:13.460 --> 01:07:15.970
I had no intention of actually letting you.

845
01:07:16.250 --> 01:07:19.469
but your efforts have earned you
these three squeezes.

846
01:07:19.470 --> 01:07:21.510
Squeeze them gratefully.

847
01:07:25.230 --> 01:07:26.930
She's an angel!

848
01:07:38.980 --> 01:07:40.770
It feels so good!

849
01:07:52.020 --> 01:07:53.169
What the...?

850
01:07:53.170 --> 01:07:55.089
Breast pads.

851
01:07:55.090 --> 01:07:58.180
A wondrous invention that
makes your bosom look bigger.

852
01:08:01.930 --> 01:08:04.310
Now! Two squeezes remain.

853
01:08:13.830 --> 01:08:15.990
And now! The final fondling!

854
01:08:19.850 --> 01:08:22.199
There. done! All done!

855
01:08:22.200 --> 01:08:25.190
What did you think? Was it not fantastic?

856
01:08:26.660 --> 01:08:29.109
How lucky for you. to grasp
such splendorous things!

857
01:08:29.110 --> 01:08:31.209
And now we are even!

858
01:08:31.210 --> 01:08:32.749
With Meowy saved.

859
01:08:32.750 --> 01:08:35.719
- I have no real reason to hunt devils any longer.
- There's lots of stuff I could say. but...

860
01:08:35.720 --> 01:08:38.219
- yet there's no escaping Makima!
- Huh?

861
01:08:38.220 --> 01:08:40.799
So I will aid you all with your duty!

862
01:08:40.800 --> 01:08:42.620
I'm sure the pleasure is all yours!

863
01:08:44.980 --> 01:08:46.720
Meowy! Off to bed we go!

864
01:08:52.940 --> 01:08:54.260
That's it?

865
01:09:01.740 --> 01:09:03.859
Seconds would be splendid!

866
01:09:03.860 --> 01:09:05.029
I'll eat yours. if you won't have it!

867
01:09:05.030 --> 01:09:05.750
You little...!

868
01:09:08.410 --> 01:09:11.250
This is the form apology
for the damage to the buildings.

869
01:09:11.530 --> 01:09:15.059
This is for verifying the disposal
of the devils' bodies.

870
01:09:15.060 --> 01:09:18.559
Then there's this. from the Ministry of Land.
Infrastructure. Transport and Tourism.

871
01:09:18.560 --> 01:09:20.760
You'll need to stamp it. here and here.

872
01:09:27.280 --> 01:09:29.819
I hate making you do all this paperwork.

873
01:09:29.820 --> 01:09:33.650
It's almost like killing
the Bat Devil was a bad thing.

874
01:09:35.760 --> 01:09:39.150
Is something bothering you. Denji?

875
01:09:42.110 --> 01:09:43.160
Y'know. I...

876
01:09:43.490 --> 01:09:47.710
There's something I was chasing after.
and I finally managed to get it.

877
01:09:48.410 --> 01:09:51.180
But once I did. it wasn't...

878
01:09:51.850 --> 01:09:54.930
as big of a deal as I thought.

879
01:09:55.420 --> 01:10:01.290
Now I'm wondering. if I go after
something else. and get my hands on it.

880
01:10:02.340 --> 01:10:07.210
am I just gonna think
I was happier during the chase?

881
01:10:09.080 --> 01:10:12.940
That's. like... total bullshit. isn't it?

882
01:10:15.380 --> 01:10:18.210
What exactly are you talking about. Denji?

883
01:10:18.570 --> 01:10:23.450
I touched boobs for the first time.
but it wasn't that great.

884
01:10:32.660 --> 01:10:34.009
Denji...

885
01:10:34.010 --> 01:10:35.630
I believe that. when it comes to sex.

886
01:10:36.060 --> 01:10:42.130
the better you understand
the other person. the better it feels.

887
01:10:44.580 --> 01:10:49.070
But it's hard to understand
how someone else feels.

888
01:10:50.620 --> 01:10:54.150
So. start with observing the hand. carefully.

889
01:10:56.390 --> 01:10:59.250
How long are their fingers?

890
01:11:02.590 --> 01:11:05.760
Are their palms cold?

891
01:11:06.490 --> 01:11:07.840
Are they warm?

892
01:11:09.450 --> 01:11:11.070
What's the shape of their ears?

893
01:11:12.010 --> 01:11:14.419
Ever had your finger bitten?

894
01:11:14.420 --> 01:11:15.669
B-Bit...?

895
01:11:15.670 --> 01:11:17.090
Remember this.

896
01:11:17.950 --> 01:11:20.860
So that even if you can't see.

897
01:11:21.800 --> 01:11:26.800
you'll be able to tell it's me.
from how hard I'm biting.

898
01:11:28.360 --> 01:11:29.660
Memorize it.

899
01:11:40.220 --> 01:11:42.280
I... got it.

900
01:12:11.540 --> 01:12:13.020
Denji...

901
01:12:14.730 --> 01:12:17.020
I'd like to ask you to do something for me.

902
01:12:17.440 --> 01:12:18.650
Can I?

903
01:12:20.820 --> 01:12:21.900
Yeah.

904
01:12:27.280 --> 01:12:29.930
I want you to beat the Gun Devil.

905
01:12:30.730 --> 01:12:32.540
Gun Devil?

906
01:12:33.160 --> 01:12:39.290
It appeared in America 13 years ago.
but nobody knows where it is now.

907
01:12:39.900 --> 01:12:45.050
It's a very strong devil
that all hunters want to kill.

908
01:12:46.650 --> 01:12:51.010
But I happen to think that you can kill it.

909
01:12:51.680 --> 01:12:56.680
Because you're not like any
of the other Devil Hunters.

910
01:12:57.270 --> 01:13:00.690
And if you're able to kill the Gun Devil.

911
01:13:01.070 --> 01:13:05.500
I'll make any wish of yours come true.

912
01:13:08.160 --> 01:13:11.179
You're saying if your Denji
kills the Gun Devil.

913
01:13:11.180 --> 01:13:16.200
Miss Makima's gonna make
any wish of his come true?

914
01:13:16.840 --> 01:13:19.680
So... like. I mean...

915
01:13:20.350 --> 01:13:22.579
You're saying if your Denji
kills the Gun Devil.

916
01:13:22.580 --> 01:13:26.460
Miss Makima's gonna make
any wish of his come true?

917
01:13:31.910 --> 01:13:34.409
Anything. like... even se—

918
01:13:34.410 --> 01:13:36.719
I said anything. Denji.

919
01:13:36.720 --> 01:13:40.230
Holy shit! Is that even allowed?!

920
01:13:41.110 --> 01:13:45.400
It's only allowed because this devil
is so strong and bad. mind you.

921
01:13:46.370 --> 01:13:50.189
Thirteen years ago. people
were trying to profit off of guns

922
01:13:50.190 --> 01:13:53.849
as a counter-measure against
devils across the world.

923
01:13:53.850 --> 01:13:58.620
which resulted in an increase in crime and conflict where they were used.

924
01:13:58.990 --> 01:14:03.460
The news focused on it non-stop for a while.

925
01:14:03.880 --> 01:14:08.720
with people more afraid
of gun violence than ever.

926
01:14:09.880 --> 01:14:14.300
Then a major armed terrorist
attack happened in America.

927
01:14:14.760 --> 01:14:17.730
That was the day the Gun Devil appeared.

928
01:14:21.640 --> 01:14:27.360
(The Country Mouse And The City Mouse)
"This is where I live." said the city mouse.

929
01:14:28.360 --> 01:14:31.859
And. oh what a big house it was!

930
01:14:31.860 --> 01:14:32.809
The city mouse's family—

931
01:14:32.810 --> 01:14:33.740
Dad!

932
01:14:34.170 --> 01:14:35.910
Let's play catch outside.

933
01:14:36.280 --> 01:14:40.450
Taiyo doesn't feel well.
Find something you can play by yourself.

934
01:14:40.820 --> 01:14:42.589
He never does.

935
01:14:42.590 --> 01:14:44.499
I don't remember him feeling good.

936
01:14:44.500 --> 01:14:48.510
You're the older brother.
Be good and play by yourself.

937
01:14:50.160 --> 01:14:51.290
I...

938
01:14:51.760 --> 01:14:54.760
I wanna play with him.

939
01:15:07.310 --> 01:15:08.570
Quit following me.

940
01:15:11.440 --> 01:15:13.950
You're so annoying... I said cut it out!

941
01:15:17.230 --> 01:15:19.150
I'm gonna play by myself.

942
01:15:23.080 --> 01:15:24.490
Gotcha!

943
01:15:26.250 --> 01:15:28.380
Stupid! I said cut it out!

944
01:15:36.380 --> 01:15:37.510
It's cold...

945
01:15:43.120 --> 01:15:46.520
If you catch a cold. I'm gonna get in trouble.

946
01:15:48.650 --> 01:15:52.220
Your hands won't get cold
if we play catch. right?

947
01:15:52.950 --> 01:15:54.760
Go grab a glove from the house.

948
01:15:56.480 --> 01:15:58.150
Yes!

949
01:16:13.300 --> 01:16:14.539
(November 18th 10:00AM)
(Gun Devil makes landfall in Japan for 26 seconds)

950
01:16:14.540 --> 01:16:17.030
(57.912 killed)
In a little under five minutes.

951
01:16:17.031 --> 01:16:19.116
(124 seconds in America. Death toll: 548012)
1.2 million people were killed.

952
01:16:19.550 --> 01:16:22.118
(7 Seconds in Canada. Death toll: 8481)
The Gun Devil hasn't been seen since.

953
01:16:22.119 --> 01:16:23.495
(37 seconds in China. Death toll: 316932.)
The Gun Devil hasn't been seen since.

954
01:16:23.496 --> 01:16:24.559
(210 seconds in the Soviet Union. Death toll: 155302.)

955
01:16:24.560 --> 01:16:25.809
(2 seconds in Mexico. Death toll: 6088.)
(0.4 seconds in Hawaii. Death toll: 780.)
(15 seconds in India. Death toll: 29950.)

956
01:16:25.810 --> 01:16:31.329
Fear of devils across the board
increased as a result.

957
01:16:31.330 --> 01:16:35.950
making them all stronger than ever before.

958
01:16:37.270 --> 01:16:41.969
Gun control got a lot more
severe. internationally.

959
01:16:41.970 --> 01:16:48.880
in an attempt to weaken the Gun Devil.
along with increased censorship of the news.

960
01:16:50.520 --> 01:16:52.619
I'm not sure I understand. but...

961
01:16:52.620 --> 01:16:55.630
Let's say this thing's so strong.
it's hard to understand.

962
01:16:56.090 --> 01:16:58.510
Do you think you can beat it. Denji?

963
01:16:59.720 --> 01:17:00.550
Well...

964
01:17:01.060 --> 01:17:04.140
If I bust out all the stops.

965
01:17:04.540 --> 01:17:06.770
it'll be a peace of cake.

966
01:17:07.660 --> 01:17:09.309
In that case...

967
01:17:09.310 --> 01:17:11.910
First. we'll need to actually
find the Gun Devil.

968
01:17:12.940 --> 01:17:15.570
How exactly are we gonna do that. anyway?

969
01:17:16.240 --> 01:17:19.820
These are pieces of the Gun Devil
that we've collected.

970
01:17:20.410 --> 01:17:25.760
It's so fast. pieces of it
are torn off just from moving.

971
01:17:26.080 --> 01:17:28.499
If a devil eats some of this.

972
01:17:28.500 --> 01:17:33.069
no matter what their nature.
they become more powerful.

973
01:17:33.070 --> 01:17:35.809
If you look at these pieces of flesh...

974
01:17:35.810 --> 01:17:37.590
See how they stick together?

975
01:17:39.040 --> 01:17:42.359
Because of how powerful the Gun Devil is.

976
01:17:42.360 --> 01:17:45.209
once the chunks of flesh
reach a certain size.

977
01:17:45.210 --> 01:17:48.810
they start to be attracted
to the original body.

978
01:17:49.600 --> 01:17:52.840
So if we can make this piece bigger.

979
01:17:53.530 --> 01:17:55.920
it'll lead us to the Gun Devil.

980
01:17:56.460 --> 01:17:57.610
Got one.

981
01:17:58.840 --> 01:18:02.240
So it really was snacking
on a piece of the Gun.

982
01:18:02.730 --> 01:18:06.240
Explains how such
a wimpy devil got so strong.

983
01:18:06.540 --> 01:18:09.430
But did it find that piece.
or did someone serve it up?

984
01:18:10.990 --> 01:18:13.750
Doesn't change what our job is.

985
01:18:14.190 --> 01:18:16.250
We keep killing devils.

986
01:18:16.820 --> 01:18:19.570
and eventually. we'll find him.

987
01:18:22.720 --> 01:18:25.010
Public Safety's received a request
for devil extermination.

988
01:18:25.350 --> 01:18:27.769
A devil has been spotted inside of a hotel.

989
01:18:27.770 --> 01:18:30.639
No confirmation on the status
of the hotel's guests.

990
01:18:30.640 --> 01:18:35.420
Several of the civilian Devil Hunters
who initially went in have been found dead.

991
01:18:35.960 --> 01:18:38.719
Activity has been observed
from the flesh chunks.

992
01:18:38.720 --> 01:18:41.390
so it's believed the target has
consumed a piece of the Gun Devil.

993
01:18:42.280 --> 01:18:46.430
We're sending six agents from Public Safety
Devil Extermination Special Division 4.

994
01:18:48.550 --> 01:18:51.500
It's hiding somewhere in this hotel.

995
01:18:52.110 --> 01:18:54.420
And this is no ordinary devil.

996
01:18:54.830 --> 01:18:57.680
The Gun Devil's flesh is being drawn towards it.

997
01:18:58.070 --> 01:19:00.919
which means this devil has eaten a piece.

998
01:19:00.920 --> 01:19:03.680
Maybe it's the Gun Devil for real?

999
01:19:04.730 --> 01:19:09.309
The more flesh. the stronger the attraction.
The reaction's not big enough.

1000
01:19:09.310 --> 01:19:11.680
How amusing... Give that thing to me!

1001
01:19:12.800 --> 01:19:15.190
I thought I told you two
to work on your manners.

1002
01:19:17.030 --> 01:19:17.779
Who the hell's gonna suck up

1003
01:19:17.780 --> 01:19:20.570
- How foolish and conceited these humans be!
- to you for no reason?

1004
01:19:23.700 --> 01:19:25.249
Mr. Hayakawa.

1005
01:19:25.250 --> 01:19:26.489
Sir.

1006
01:19:26.490 --> 01:19:27.459
Good.

1007
01:19:27.460 --> 01:19:28.700
Sweet!

1008
01:19:29.600 --> 01:19:30.529
Dude. he's so easy.

1009
01:19:30.530 --> 01:19:31.580
Hayakawa!

1010
01:19:32.010 --> 01:19:34.759
Considering we're about
to fight some devils...

1011
01:19:34.760 --> 01:19:37.460
Can we really trust these two
to watch our backs?

1012
01:19:37.870 --> 01:19:41.069
One's a Fiend. and the other is some punk...

1013
01:19:41.070 --> 01:19:43.030
I'm not sure about this.

1014
01:19:44.090 --> 01:19:46.470
We can't let them watch our backs.

1015
01:19:46.780 --> 01:19:50.339
On extermination missions.
they'll be taking point.

1016
01:19:50.340 --> 01:19:54.410
If they try to run or
switch sides. we kill them.

1017
01:19:54.800 --> 01:19:56.849
You're treating us like livestock!

1018
01:19:56.850 --> 01:19:59.480
You two don't get rights.

1019
01:20:00.570 --> 01:20:02.729
He's super pissed.

1020
01:20:02.730 --> 01:20:04.229
Must be from this morning.

1021
01:20:04.230 --> 01:20:06.609
Perhaps our prank went too far?

1022
01:20:06.610 --> 01:20:09.709
You call that a prank?! I could kill you!

1023
01:20:09.710 --> 01:20:11.950
Yikes! What happened?

1024
01:20:12.390 --> 01:20:16.079
Aki. you can't just be harsh
all the time. y'know?

1025
01:20:16.080 --> 01:20:20.109
She's right! The bat almost killed me.
and now there's more work?!

1026
01:20:20.110 --> 01:20:21.210
I want a reward!

1027
01:20:22.710 --> 01:20:25.710
Got it! I'll take one for the team.

1028
01:20:26.220 --> 01:20:29.139
Whoever kills this devil will win...

1029
01:20:29.140 --> 01:20:32.220
a kiss on the cheek from yours truly!

1030
01:20:33.600 --> 01:20:36.669
That's... You shouldn't do that!

1031
01:20:36.670 --> 01:20:38.980
A young woman who's not married
shouldn't be so... indecent!

1032
01:20:40.590 --> 01:20:43.279
But doesn't a reward help with motivation?

1033
01:20:43.280 --> 01:20:44.900
Right?

1034
01:20:50.010 --> 01:20:51.779
I'm not gonna sweat the kisses.

1035
01:20:51.780 --> 01:20:54.539
Don't worry about it. I'm plenty motivated.

1036
01:20:54.540 --> 01:20:55.699
Oh?

1037
01:20:55.700 --> 01:20:58.880
I got my sights set on someone
for a first kiss already.

1038
01:20:59.430 --> 01:21:03.419
I'm gonna find all these meat chunks
or whatever for her.

1039
01:21:03.420 --> 01:21:06.670
So. until the Gun Devil's dead.
no smooching for me.

1040
01:21:08.900 --> 01:21:11.079
That's a hell of a thing
to say in front of Aki!

1041
01:21:11.080 --> 01:21:13.890
Besides. I learned something real important.

1042
01:21:14.650 --> 01:21:19.090
Sex stuff feels better when it's
two people who get each other.

1043
01:21:19.400 --> 01:21:23.150
I don't even know your name.
so I ain't after your lips!

1044
01:21:27.080 --> 01:21:30.620
Then. if you kill the devil. Denji...

1045
01:21:31.780 --> 01:21:33.990
I'll give you a kiss... with tongue.

1046
01:21:41.580 --> 01:21:43.999
It's dangerous to run off solo! Stop!

1047
01:21:44.000 --> 01:21:44.699
(8th Floor)

1048
01:21:44.700 --> 01:21:47.880
Damn. I love teasing boys!

1049
01:21:48.170 --> 01:21:50.269
Oh man. what are we gonna do?

1050
01:21:50.270 --> 01:21:51.889
I yearn for blood.

1051
01:21:51.890 --> 01:21:54.810
It's dangerous! You need to stop!

1052
01:21:57.340 --> 01:22:01.349
Himeno's been nice enough to
train me for the last six months!

1053
01:22:01.350 --> 01:22:04.529
If the alternative is letting
some thug like you kiss her...

1054
01:22:04.530 --> 01:22:06.569
Then I'll take that kiss on the cheek!

1055
01:22:06.570 --> 01:22:07.489
Move!

1056
01:22:07.490 --> 01:22:09.929
I don't want some dude
all over me! It's nasty!

1057
01:22:09.930 --> 01:22:10.869
Say what?!

1058
01:22:10.870 --> 01:22:13.620
- Die! I'm after a way bigger goal than you. dude
- I wish to join you!

1059
01:22:14.640 --> 01:22:15.419
Shut up!

1060
01:22:15.420 --> 01:22:18.850
What's your take on the rookies. Himeno?

1061
01:22:20.740 --> 01:22:24.380
I'd say Arai's not super competent.
but makes up for it in motivation.

1062
01:22:24.730 --> 01:22:26.419
Meanwhile. Kobeni's got the moves.

1063
01:22:26.420 --> 01:22:27.910
but she's really timid.

1064
01:22:28.460 --> 01:22:32.450
You think any of the four rookies
have a shot of surviving. Aki?

1065
01:22:34.120 --> 01:22:36.479
Most people either die

1066
01:22:36.480 --> 01:22:37.953
or go private after a year.

1067
01:22:38.510 --> 01:22:39.829
regardless of how strong

1068
01:22:39.830 --> 01:22:42.190
I thought they were.

1069
01:22:42.830 --> 01:22:45.440
That's not really an answer.

1070
01:22:46.870 --> 01:22:48.780
Don't die on me. Aki.

1071
01:22:57.060 --> 01:22:58.120
Himeno...

1072
01:22:59.220 --> 01:23:01.520
This is your new partner.

1073
01:23:02.360 --> 01:23:05.549
He's rude. but I trained him
to be of some use.

1074
01:23:05.550 --> 01:23:06.890
Try and get along.

1075
01:23:12.380 --> 01:23:13.530
I'm Aki.

1076
01:23:14.010 --> 01:23:15.140
Nice to meet you.

1077
01:23:20.390 --> 01:23:22.010
Are you gonna be any help?

1078
01:23:23.990 --> 01:23:26.520
Well... I think so.

1079
01:23:27.500 --> 01:23:30.699
You're gonna be my sixth partner.

1080
01:23:30.700 --> 01:23:32.330
The others all died.

1081
01:23:33.070 --> 01:23:35.680
They all died because they were useless.

1082
01:23:39.340 --> 01:23:41.410
Don't die on me. Aki.

1083
01:23:42.420 --> 01:23:46.920
Gotta say. I'm not seeing
any devils around here.

1084
01:23:47.290 --> 01:23:50.700
Does that meat chunk of yours even work?

1085
01:23:52.920 --> 01:23:54.909
So tired...

1086
01:23:54.910 --> 01:23:56.140
Aki...

1087
01:23:57.360 --> 01:23:58.430
Incoming.

1088
01:24:17.840 --> 01:24:18.820
Got it.

1089
01:24:19.950 --> 01:24:21.109
It floats?!

1090
01:24:21.110 --> 01:24:22.910
The battle is joined!

1091
01:24:30.380 --> 01:24:34.190
Damnable devil! Did you see
how it floated in fear of me?!

1092
01:24:35.160 --> 01:24:37.259
No. no. that's my power.

1093
01:24:37.260 --> 01:24:38.519
Say what?

1094
01:24:38.520 --> 01:24:41.579
I've got a contract with the Ghost Devil.

1095
01:24:41.580 --> 01:24:46.769
I served up my right eye in exchange
for being able to use a ghost's right hand.

1096
01:24:46.770 --> 01:24:51.160
My ghost hand's invisible and strong.
Pretty slick. right?

1097
01:24:52.150 --> 01:24:55.429
How about it. Aki?
Has he got any of the Gun's flesh?

1098
01:24:55.430 --> 01:24:58.779
No strong reaction. This isn't the one.

1099
01:24:58.780 --> 01:25:02.240
I see... guess we better keep heading up.

1100
01:25:03.990 --> 01:25:08.849
Is it wise to blather on about
your powers in my presence?

1101
01:25:08.850 --> 01:25:12.069
Are you people not meant to hold my reins?

1102
01:25:12.070 --> 01:25:14.550
Knowing about our powers makes
for better teamwork. right?

1103
01:25:15.130 --> 01:25:18.449
Besides. I've got a few tricks
up my sleeve. so I'm not worried.

1104
01:25:18.450 --> 01:25:20.359
Truly?

1105
01:25:20.360 --> 01:25:23.350
So what would you do if I said
I was going to kill this one?

1106
01:25:24.640 --> 01:25:26.509
Put the weapon away.

1107
01:25:26.510 --> 01:25:29.520
If you misbehave.
I can always choke you to death.

1108
01:25:32.260 --> 01:25:34.020
Can't... touch it...

1109
01:25:40.400 --> 01:25:43.090
I'd prefer if we got along. It's easier!

1110
01:25:45.110 --> 01:25:47.269
I will devour you in time!

1111
01:25:47.270 --> 01:25:49.540
You better not. I'm trying to get a kiss.

1112
01:25:49.890 --> 01:25:54.110
Do you guys not get that the devil
is still around? Can't you pipe...

1113
01:25:56.950 --> 01:25:57.970
Huh?

1114
01:26:03.830 --> 01:26:04.430
What is it?

1115
01:26:04.840 --> 01:26:09.809
We were... on our way to
the 9th floor from the 8th. right?

1116
01:26:09.810 --> 01:26:10.810
(8th Floor)
Yeah.

1117
01:26:12.430 --> 01:26:14.200
But this is the 8th floor.

1118
01:26:15.570 --> 01:26:17.319
You probably read it wrong.

1119
01:26:17.320 --> 01:26:19.999
It's not that! Something's going on here!

1120
01:26:20.000 --> 01:26:21.069
I'm gonna double check.

1121
01:26:21.070 --> 01:26:23.629
I know! Grilled like a steak!

1122
01:26:23.630 --> 01:26:24.719
Steak?!

1123
01:26:24.720 --> 01:26:26.730
I wanna try steak!

1124
01:26:29.690 --> 01:26:30.700
Huh?

1125
01:26:33.460 --> 01:26:37.560
Arai... just now... you were
going downstairs. right?

1126
01:26:46.680 --> 01:26:49.610
Kobeni. make a double peace sign and stay put.

1127
01:26:56.070 --> 01:26:57.570
Well. shit.

1128
01:27:01.830 --> 01:27:04.699
Aki... what's going on here?

1129
01:27:04.700 --> 01:27:07.500
It has to be a devil's power at work.

1130
01:27:08.580 --> 01:27:10.430
Kobeni. stand right there.

1131
01:27:23.070 --> 01:27:25.440
Why are there rooms
on the other side of the window?

1132
01:27:31.560 --> 01:27:34.189
Hey! None of the windows go anywhere!

1133
01:27:34.190 --> 01:27:36.080
They just open to the room across the hall!

1134
01:27:37.050 --> 01:27:38.640
I figured as much.

1135
01:27:39.390 --> 01:27:41.029
We're trapped on the eighth floor.

1136
01:27:41.030 --> 01:27:41.649
(8th Floor)
We're trapped on the eighth floor.

1137
01:27:41.650 --> 01:27:43.842
We're trapped on the eighth floor.

1138
01:27:51.790 --> 01:27:53.619
Let's run through what we know.

1139
01:27:53.620 --> 01:27:55.869
This is probably a devil's doing.

1140
01:27:55.870 --> 01:27:58.619
and no matter how many times
we try to go to a different floor.

1141
01:27:58.620 --> 01:28:00.249
we end up on the eighth again.

1142
01:28:00.250 --> 01:28:02.630
The elevator is inoperable
for whatever reason.

1143
01:28:02.980 --> 01:28:05.630
There's no way outside via
the rooms or any windows.

1144
01:28:06.040 --> 01:28:09.600
We tried going through the ceiling.
but ended up on the eighth floor again.

1145
01:28:10.730 --> 01:28:14.330
Maybe it's because Power killed that devil?

1146
01:28:14.770 --> 01:28:17.639
He coulda died while using
the power to keep us trapped.

1147
01:28:17.640 --> 01:28:18.609
And now—

1148
01:28:18.610 --> 01:28:20.239
You commanded me to kill him!

1149
01:28:20.240 --> 01:28:21.239
Did not!

1150
01:28:21.240 --> 01:28:25.149
A devil's powers are released
when they die. It can't be that.

1151
01:28:25.150 --> 01:28:27.910
Is the flesh piece reacting. Aki?

1152
01:28:28.220 --> 01:28:29.410
Actually...

1153
01:28:29.800 --> 01:28:32.190
It's gone dead still.

1154
01:28:32.830 --> 01:28:37.219
That devil before was bait. and we bit hard.

1155
01:28:37.220 --> 01:28:40.629
I've never seen a devil try
something so clever before.

1156
01:28:40.630 --> 01:28:43.879
But if no one hears from us for a while.

1157
01:28:43.880 --> 01:28:47.010
won't other Devil Hunters show up to help?

1158
01:28:48.680 --> 01:28:53.440
I guess we better hope they don't
fall into the same kind of trap. then.

1159
01:28:55.160 --> 01:28:58.739
We're all gonna die here.

1160
01:28:58.740 --> 01:29:01.399
We're gonna starve to death.

1161
01:29:01.400 --> 01:29:03.799
H-Hang in there. Kobeni!

1162
01:29:03.800 --> 01:29:07.499
Didn't you become a Devil Hunter
to send your brother to college?!

1163
01:29:07.500 --> 01:29:09.779
They basically forced me to do it.

1164
01:29:09.780 --> 01:29:12.229
My parents are set on my
older brother going to college.

1165
01:29:12.230 --> 01:29:14.189
since he's the gifted one.

1166
01:29:14.190 --> 01:29:16.290
So they made me get a job.

1167
01:29:16.760 --> 01:29:21.340
It was become a Devil Hunter or a sex worker!

1168
01:29:24.000 --> 01:29:27.799
I wanted to go to college. too!

1169
01:29:27.800 --> 01:29:32.080
And now I'm gonna die here!

1170
01:29:37.020 --> 01:29:38.430
Her face...!

1171
01:29:40.150 --> 01:29:41.650
Enough!

1172
01:29:41.900 --> 01:29:43.260
Quit laughing!

1173
01:29:43.990 --> 01:29:48.370
Kobeni. devils love fear. okay?

1174
01:29:48.740 --> 01:29:51.909
If you get scared. you're giving them
what they want. sweetie.

1175
01:29:51.910 --> 01:29:55.090
But I'm so scared!

1176
01:29:56.190 --> 01:29:58.080
Something bothering you. too. Aki?

1177
01:30:00.580 --> 01:30:01.960
The clocks in this room...

1178
01:30:02.870 --> 01:30:05.709
have been stuck at 8:18 for a while now.

1179
01:30:05.710 --> 01:30:09.470
In every single room... it's 8:18.

1180
01:30:11.750 --> 01:30:17.349
There's a chance that time has been
frozen here on the eighth floor.

1181
01:30:17.350 --> 01:30:20.830
And if that's the case. no one is coming.

1182
01:30:21.980 --> 01:30:25.110
Oh. shit! Then we can sleep all we want. right?

1183
01:30:26.660 --> 01:30:28.789
How stupid are you?

1184
01:30:28.790 --> 01:30:33.129
We might be trapped in here forever.

1185
01:30:33.130 --> 01:30:36.729
I mean. we might be. but
we might not be. too. y'know?

1186
01:30:36.730 --> 01:30:38.120
Wake me when you figure it out.

1187
01:30:38.550 --> 01:30:41.870
This bed is freaking sweet.
It'd be stupid not to sleep in it.

1188
01:30:42.300 --> 01:30:45.130
I owe the devil for this nap.

1189
01:30:52.860 --> 01:30:54.220
He's actually asleep...

1190
01:30:58.200 --> 01:30:59.519
Denji.

1191
01:30:59.520 --> 01:31:02.150
Rise and shine. Denji.

1192
01:31:08.750 --> 01:31:11.659
We find a way off the eighth floor yet?

1193
01:31:11.660 --> 01:31:13.780
Hate to break it to you. but not yet.

1194
01:31:14.260 --> 01:31:18.629
We found out the power and electricity
are still working while you were asleep.

1195
01:31:18.630 --> 01:31:23.789
There was a little bit of food that some of
the guests who ran must've left behind.

1196
01:31:23.790 --> 01:31:27.670
I'll be honest. everyone's really worn out.

1197
01:31:28.190 --> 01:31:31.170
Aki's been searching for the devil nonstop.

1198
01:31:31.620 --> 01:31:34.800
I told him to take a break.
but he won't listen.

1199
01:31:35.180 --> 01:31:38.699
Arai was helping Aki at first.

1200
01:31:38.700 --> 01:31:42.310
but now he's locked himself up in
another room to have a panic attack.

1201
01:31:42.660 --> 01:31:47.310
Kobeni freaked out and tried to drink
toilet bowl water. so I knocked her out.

1202
01:31:47.630 --> 01:31:49.940
And as for the Fiend...

1203
01:31:50.320 --> 01:31:52.189
Something happen to Power?

1204
01:31:52.190 --> 01:31:55.199
Given there's nothing else to do.
I've decided to win the Nobel Prize!

1205
01:31:55.200 --> 01:31:59.789
Once I've earned such glorious esteem.
the humans will all kowtow to me!

1206
01:31:59.790 --> 01:32:02.539
And with the Nobel Prize as my foothold.

1207
01:32:02.540 --> 01:32:04.479
I shall ascend to the prime minister's throne!

1208
01:32:04.480 --> 01:32:07.670
What better way to ensure human suffering?

1209
01:32:08.090 --> 01:32:11.410
My first act will be passing a 100% sales tax!

1210
01:32:12.480 --> 01:32:13.789
She's always like that.

1211
01:32:13.790 --> 01:32:16.430
Huh. Okay. then.

1212
01:32:16.840 --> 01:32:19.689
Let's take turns watching Kobeni and Arai.

1213
01:32:19.690 --> 01:32:22.140
I couldn't even use the bathroom
when it was just me.

1214
01:32:36.880 --> 01:32:39.699
Well. this is my last cigarette.

1215
01:32:39.700 --> 01:32:42.489
I'm bored by how little this upsets you.

1216
01:32:42.490 --> 01:32:47.459
I can take it easy because
Aki's working hard.

1217
01:32:47.460 --> 01:32:49.840
The nicotine also helps!

1218
01:32:50.100 --> 01:32:53.590
Gotta have a port in a storm. right?

1219
01:32:53.840 --> 01:32:57.339
Life is sweeter with a bit of dependence.

1220
01:32:57.340 --> 01:32:59.830
Hey. that's the same brand he smokes.

1221
01:33:02.870 --> 01:33:06.179
That's because Aki learned all
about the flavor of cigarettes

1222
01:33:06.180 --> 01:33:07.940
from yours truly!

1223
01:33:09.400 --> 01:33:11.899
There's something my master said...

1224
01:33:11.900 --> 01:33:17.559
Devils don't fear Devil Hunters
who are strong or brave.

1225
01:33:17.560 --> 01:33:20.410
They fear Devil Hunters who have a screw loose.

1226
01:33:20.670 --> 01:33:23.570
Which is why I think you'll survive
a long time in this job. Aki.

1227
01:33:25.320 --> 01:33:26.679
Was that an insult?

1228
01:33:26.680 --> 01:33:29.360
And I'll eat your almond tofu
if you don't want it.

1229
01:33:32.210 --> 01:33:33.650
Just one.

1230
01:33:35.210 --> 01:33:37.300
I'm not smoking. It's bad for your bones.

1231
01:33:38.730 --> 01:33:42.810
I wish you would. I get the feeling
we're gonna be together for a while.

1232
01:33:52.170 --> 01:33:54.039
Just one. then.

1233
01:33:54.040 --> 01:33:57.280
This is the first and last cigarette
I ever light up.

1234
01:33:59.430 --> 01:34:01.989
Himeno. do you have any smokes left?

1235
01:34:01.990 --> 01:34:04.989
Sorry. Last one.

1236
01:34:04.990 --> 01:34:07.290
Let me have it. please.

1237
01:34:09.260 --> 01:34:11.210
If you insist...

1238
01:34:13.130 --> 01:34:15.549
Dude. that's kissing! No fair!
That's an indirect kiss!

1239
01:34:15.550 --> 01:34:16.950
Shut up.

1240
01:34:20.410 --> 01:34:22.140
I've got bad news.

1241
01:34:23.110 --> 01:34:25.179
Remember the devil we killed?

1242
01:34:25.180 --> 01:34:27.180
The one that I slew!

1243
01:34:27.470 --> 01:34:30.400
Well. he's a lot bigger now.

1244
01:34:40.400 --> 01:34:43.160
That really is the one I slew.

1245
01:34:43.460 --> 01:34:47.569
It traps us in a hotel...
and its body turns into that?

1246
01:34:47.570 --> 01:34:49.340
What the hell kind of devil is this?

1247
01:34:50.460 --> 01:34:53.309
Humans. Hear me. humans.

1248
01:34:53.310 --> 01:34:57.799
You foolish humans.
I offer you a contract...

1249
01:34:57.800 --> 01:34:59.299
It talked!

1250
01:34:59.300 --> 01:35:00.779
A contract?

1251
01:35:00.780 --> 01:35:04.329
Feed me the human known as Denji.

1252
01:35:04.330 --> 01:35:06.099
Even his corpse will do.

1253
01:35:06.100 --> 01:35:07.679
Let me eat him.

1254
01:35:07.680 --> 01:35:12.310
Do this. and I'll let the rest
of you leave in peace.

1255
01:35:12.590 --> 01:35:15.979
You'll be free to leave!
Now. accept this contract!

1256
01:35:15.980 --> 01:35:20.320
Do it... Do it...

1257
01:35:26.860 --> 01:35:29.240
Denji... let it eat you.

1258
01:35:49.940 --> 01:35:51.479
Man. that's obnoxious.

1259
01:35:51.480 --> 01:35:54.900
Aki. can't you swallow
this thing with the Fox Devil?

1260
01:35:55.450 --> 01:35:56.450
Kon.

1261
01:35:58.670 --> 01:36:00.889
Looks like Fox Devil isn't coming.

1262
01:36:00.890 --> 01:36:03.309
We're cut off from the rest of the world.

1263
01:36:03.310 --> 01:36:06.109
The Fox Devil's body is in Kyoto.
so that makes sense.

1264
01:36:06.110 --> 01:36:09.130
Let's see what my Ghost can do. then.

1265
01:36:11.140 --> 01:36:11.999
That hurt!

1266
01:36:12.000 --> 01:36:16.750
It hurts! Oh. it hurts! The pain!

1267
01:36:18.880 --> 01:36:21.799
It hurts...! It hurts!

1268
01:36:21.800 --> 01:36:23.310
It got even bigger!

1269
01:36:24.460 --> 01:36:25.799
It's pointless!

1270
01:36:25.800 --> 01:36:29.049
This isn't my main body...

1271
01:36:29.050 --> 01:36:31.809
You won't find my heart here.

1272
01:36:31.810 --> 01:36:34.189
You're inside of my stomach...

1273
01:36:34.190 --> 01:36:38.059
and I have no weaknesses
on this eighth floor.

1274
01:36:38.060 --> 01:36:42.070
There is no way to survive this place.
apart from accepting my offer.

1275
01:36:43.370 --> 01:36:47.049
You're probably not gonna
let them go. even if I do die.

1276
01:36:47.050 --> 01:36:48.569
Actually. no.

1277
01:36:48.570 --> 01:36:51.899
The devil used the word "contract." right?

1278
01:36:51.900 --> 01:36:56.079
Those kinds of terms hold a strong sway
when a devil is involved.

1279
01:36:56.080 --> 01:37:01.589
If one side makes good on the deal.
the other has to or else.

1280
01:37:01.590 --> 01:37:04.209
Whichever side breaks
the contract ends up dying.

1281
01:37:04.210 --> 01:37:07.400
So. we would be able to leave
by killing you. Denji.

1282
01:37:07.950 --> 01:37:11.350
Himeno... we should kill him.

1283
01:37:11.830 --> 01:37:15.849
We can come up with another plan
once he's dead. and we're out of here.

1284
01:37:15.850 --> 01:37:18.599
We're all gonna end up starving otherwise.

1285
01:37:18.600 --> 01:37:23.229
Devil Hunters are legally allowed to
make contracts with devils.

1286
01:37:23.230 --> 01:37:25.779
We should take the deal!

1287
01:37:25.780 --> 01:37:28.410
The devil wants Denji dead.

1288
01:37:28.790 --> 01:37:32.109
That means his death would benefit it.

1289
01:37:32.110 --> 01:37:33.929
which is why we're not accepting.

1290
01:37:33.930 --> 01:37:35.539
I'm with him!

1291
01:37:35.540 --> 01:37:36.829
But...

1292
01:37:36.830 --> 01:37:38.590
I say we kill him!

1293
01:37:39.420 --> 01:37:44.219
My Nobel Prize will remain forever out
of reach if I'm unable to leave this place!

1294
01:37:44.220 --> 01:37:46.049
You must die for my Nobel.

1295
01:37:46.050 --> 01:37:48.719
Fiends can't make pacts with devils.

1296
01:37:48.720 --> 01:37:52.760
It wouldn't be obligated to let us leave.
even if you killed him.

1297
01:37:53.130 --> 01:37:56.960
Look. we're not killing Denji.
We're Devil Hunters.

1298
01:37:57.790 --> 01:38:00.020
We only kill devils.

1299
01:38:02.660 --> 01:38:04.379
Shall we wrestle to pass the time. then?

1300
01:38:04.380 --> 01:38:06.530
You're just gonna try and kill me! Hell no!

1301
01:38:13.020 --> 01:38:14.469
So hungry...

1302
01:38:14.470 --> 01:38:18.789
Aki. have you got any kind of plan
for actually getting us out of here?

1303
01:38:18.790 --> 01:38:23.169
If what the devil says is true.
we can't kill it.

1304
01:38:23.170 --> 01:38:25.919
But we're not killing Denji. either.

1305
01:38:25.920 --> 01:38:29.130
So. is the plan to starve. then?

1306
01:38:31.800 --> 01:38:33.969
If we really run out of options.
I'll use the sword.

1307
01:38:33.970 --> 01:38:35.010
No. you won't.

1308
01:38:36.490 --> 01:38:39.139
If that thing can get us out of here.

1309
01:38:39.140 --> 01:38:40.610
shouldn't he use it?

1310
01:38:41.710 --> 01:38:44.650
He shouldn't use it.
even if we're out of options.

1311
01:38:45.190 --> 01:38:47.010
If it comes to that... sorry.

1312
01:38:47.530 --> 01:38:49.530
but you'll have to die. Denji!

1313
01:38:51.780 --> 01:38:53.529
It's gone?!

1314
01:38:53.530 --> 01:38:56.530
It's gone... all the food
that was left on the bed...

1315
01:38:56.860 --> 01:38:58.290
None of it's left.

1316
01:38:58.810 --> 01:38:59.830
Why?

1317
01:39:04.380 --> 01:39:07.349
You ate all of it. didn't you?

1318
01:39:07.350 --> 01:39:09.919
'Twas not me. This is Denji's doing.

1319
01:39:09.920 --> 01:39:11.999
Of all the obvious lies...

1320
01:39:12.000 --> 01:39:13.429
I get it now...

1321
01:39:13.430 --> 01:39:16.430
I figured it out.

1322
01:39:16.980 --> 01:39:21.039
We can't get out of here
because of that Fiend's power!

1323
01:39:21.040 --> 01:39:22.809
That has to be it!

1324
01:39:22.810 --> 01:39:23.689
No. it doesn't.

1325
01:39:23.690 --> 01:39:26.149
Calm down. Kobeni! This is the Blood Fiend—

1326
01:39:26.150 --> 01:39:30.779
So you're taking her side?
Even though we're Devil Hunters?!

1327
01:39:30.780 --> 01:39:33.879
You're on the devil's side. Arai!

1328
01:39:33.880 --> 01:39:35.909
You're a spy!

1329
01:39:35.910 --> 01:39:37.029
He's spycy.

1330
01:39:37.030 --> 01:39:39.370
I... I'm not on the devil's side...

1331
01:39:40.260 --> 01:39:43.920
I know you're a spy!

1332
01:39:47.170 --> 01:39:48.249
Was that a scream?

1333
01:39:48.250 --> 01:39:49.720
We need to move!

1334
01:39:58.040 --> 01:39:59.679
Kill Denji...

1335
01:39:59.680 --> 01:40:03.379
Give me his heart... Give it!

1336
01:40:03.380 --> 01:40:08.510
I will grow as your fear grows...
and with your terror. I will capture you!

1337
01:40:09.070 --> 01:40:12.319
Your deaths are a foregone conclusion!

1338
01:40:12.320 --> 01:40:14.919
So. fear me more!

1339
01:40:14.920 --> 01:40:16.889
Be overcome by your impending death!

1340
01:40:16.890 --> 01:40:19.209
Dread everything.

1341
01:40:19.210 --> 01:40:22.699
I will be the one to kill Chainsaw...

1342
01:40:22.700 --> 01:40:24.539
It will be me!

1343
01:40:24.540 --> 01:40:27.340
The Eternity Devil!

1344
01:40:33.210 --> 01:40:34.720
The floor's tilting!

1345
01:40:50.160 --> 01:40:53.619
Give me Denji's heart!

1346
01:40:53.620 --> 01:40:56.989
Somebody. anybody. kill Denji!

1347
01:40:56.990 --> 01:40:58.589
Please make him dead!

1348
01:40:58.590 --> 01:41:00.069
We're running out of time!

1349
01:41:00.070 --> 01:41:02.290
Let's just feed him to the devil!

1350
01:41:04.410 --> 01:41:05.749
I'm using the sword.

1351
01:41:05.750 --> 01:41:08.880
You okay with that. Himeno?

1352
01:41:09.290 --> 01:41:10.710
Himeno?!

1353
01:41:11.500 --> 01:41:14.679
Whoa. lady! What the hell?!

1354
01:41:14.680 --> 01:41:18.130
We can probably get out of here
if he uses that sword.

1355
01:41:18.480 --> 01:41:22.390
but the pact is one that takes a lot
of years off Aki's life in exchange.

1356
01:41:22.870 --> 01:41:26.589
He's got too much to live for.

1357
01:41:26.590 --> 01:41:28.860
I'm sorry. Denji.

1358
01:41:29.650 --> 01:41:31.400
Damn it!

1359
01:41:31.740 --> 01:41:33.269
Hey. get off!

1360
01:41:33.270 --> 01:41:34.570
Let me go!

1361
01:41:38.820 --> 01:41:41.050
Die!

1362
01:42:06.320 --> 01:42:12.490
He might be a piece of shit that
deserves being stabbed a time or two...

1363
01:42:12.990 --> 01:42:15.550
But he wants the Gun Devil dead.

1364
01:42:16.230 --> 01:42:20.210
And I... can't kill it by myself.

1365
01:42:20.760 --> 01:42:25.960
To do that. I need Devil Hunters
with the guts to fight it.

1366
01:42:26.320 --> 01:42:28.440
The more. the better...

1367
01:42:29.420 --> 01:42:31.630
Even if it costs some of my own life...

1368
01:42:32.630 --> 01:42:35.250
I'm not letting Denji die.

1369
01:42:36.650 --> 01:42:39.009
Power! You're the Blood Fiend. right?

1370
01:42:39.010 --> 01:42:41.509
Can you keep him from bleeding out?

1371
01:42:41.510 --> 01:42:45.209
I only have total control over my own blood.

1372
01:42:45.210 --> 01:42:47.430
The blood of others is a challenge.

1373
01:42:49.340 --> 01:42:53.689
But I suppose I'd need a
new cook if topknot died.

1374
01:42:53.690 --> 01:42:56.070
Given that. I have little choice.

1375
01:43:01.760 --> 01:43:03.199
What do we do?

1376
01:43:03.200 --> 01:43:04.779
What do we do?!

1377
01:43:04.780 --> 01:43:08.240
Aki... Aki! Aki. what do we do?!

1378
01:43:08.620 --> 01:43:11.409
I-It's not my fault!

1379
01:43:11.410 --> 01:43:14.379
You! This is because of you!

1380
01:43:14.380 --> 01:43:18.600
If you just let it eat you.
this would all be over!

1381
01:43:19.610 --> 01:43:21.379
Yeah. yeah. I get it.

1382
01:43:21.380 --> 01:43:23.750
Guess it's snack time. then.

1383
01:43:24.280 --> 01:43:26.300
Oh. thank goodness.

1384
01:43:27.150 --> 01:43:29.770
I'm not gonna go down smooth. though.

1385
01:43:30.480 --> 01:43:34.150
So if I manage to kill this fucking devil...

1386
01:43:34.500 --> 01:43:37.720
I still expect to get that kiss!

1387
01:43:38.650 --> 01:43:40.900
Have you any plan to win?

1388
01:43:41.270 --> 01:43:44.910
It's gonna hurt real bad.
but I'll get my chainsaws out.

1389
01:43:45.350 --> 01:43:47.099
Ch-Chainsaws?

1390
01:43:47.100 --> 01:43:52.360
I dunno what this devil's deal is.
but it's scared of my chainsaws.

1391
01:43:52.810 --> 01:43:57.280
That's why it didn't try to kill me.
and wanted you guys to do it instead.

1392
01:43:58.310 --> 01:44:03.390
And I remember it was crying
about pain when it got attacked...

1393
01:44:04.070 --> 01:44:08.430
So I figure. if I tear it up until
it can't take the pain no more.

1394
01:44:08.820 --> 01:44:10.950
it'll wanna kill itself!

1395
01:44:12.970 --> 01:44:14.980
A very devilish idea indeed.

1396
01:44:18.230 --> 01:44:20.980
I can't believe you did that for me.

1397
01:44:21.290 --> 01:44:24.140
Nobody asked you. Asshole.

1398
01:44:24.760 --> 01:44:29.090
I'm through with owing
anybody anything. got it?

1399
01:44:29.780 --> 01:44:32.390
So once you're out of here. we're even!

1400
01:44:43.210 --> 01:44:44.600
It's over...

1401
01:44:58.040 --> 01:45:02.310
I knew you were alive. Chainsaw!

1402
01:45:06.160 --> 01:45:08.940
Yeow!

1403
01:45:09.350 --> 01:45:11.470
All better!

1404
01:45:12.170 --> 01:45:14.099
This is pointless. Chainsaw!

1405
01:45:14.100 --> 01:45:15.119
The pain!

1406
01:45:15.120 --> 01:45:16.619
It hurts!

1407
01:45:16.620 --> 01:45:19.379
You won't find my heart in here!

1408
01:45:19.380 --> 01:45:21.660
You can't kill me!

1409
01:45:31.160 --> 01:45:32.140
A devil?!

1410
01:45:32.540 --> 01:45:34.140
This bodes ill.

1411
01:45:34.620 --> 01:45:37.069
Denji's losing blood ceaselessly.

1412
01:45:37.070 --> 01:45:40.520
When he's lost too much.
his chainsaws will retract.

1413
01:45:46.150 --> 01:45:49.419
You are so much weaker now.

1414
01:45:49.420 --> 01:45:51.990
How far you have fallen. Chainsaw?!

1415
01:45:59.460 --> 01:46:01.579
My chainsaws are in?

1416
01:46:01.580 --> 01:46:03.459
Need more blood!

1417
01:46:03.460 --> 01:46:05.179
You've failed!

1418
01:46:05.180 --> 01:46:06.069
Die!

1419
01:46:06.070 --> 01:46:07.590
Chainsaw!

1420
01:46:16.760 --> 01:46:19.809
This blood might seriously taste like shit...

1421
01:46:19.810 --> 01:46:23.519
But watching you shriek in pain...

1422
01:46:23.520 --> 01:46:27.230
Makes it sweet like strawberry jam!

1423
01:46:27.940 --> 01:46:30.860
The hunters that devils fear...

1424
01:46:34.620 --> 01:46:37.580
are the ones with a couple of screws loose.

1425
01:46:38.170 --> 01:46:40.830
Sahara had his head on straight...

1426
01:46:41.680 --> 01:46:43.580
So he died.

1427
01:46:43.910 --> 01:46:49.219
Same goes for Kinouchi.
and Subaru. and Sasaki. All sane.

1428
01:46:49.220 --> 01:46:53.049
They were reasonable enough
to fear attacks from a devil.

1429
01:46:53.050 --> 01:46:55.970
and that fear made the devils stronger.

1430
01:46:56.830 --> 01:47:00.450
You been working with Aki for a while now.
What do you think about him?

1431
01:47:01.410 --> 01:47:02.479
Is his head on straight?

1432
01:47:02.480 --> 01:47:07.470
I wouldn't say that about anyone
who's trying to kill the Gun Devil.

1433
01:47:07.990 --> 01:47:12.240
Didn't you join Public Safety because
you were after the Gun Devil. too?

1434
01:47:12.750 --> 01:47:15.550
You got any screws loose?

1435
01:47:16.460 --> 01:47:17.870
No. sir.

1436
01:47:18.180 --> 01:47:19.469
Exactly.

1437
01:47:19.470 --> 01:47:25.380
Most hunters. including you.
are out to put the Gun Devil down.

1438
01:47:25.630 --> 01:47:28.459
They're earnest. Honest. Straightforward.

1439
01:47:28.460 --> 01:47:32.630
And that means the devils know
exactly how to fuck with them.

1440
01:47:33.080 --> 01:47:37.890
But there's no telling what
a crazy person's thinking.

1441
01:47:38.150 --> 01:47:41.580
And even devils are afraid
of what they don't understand.

1442
01:47:44.200 --> 01:47:46.519
You're drinking too much again. master.

1443
01:47:46.520 --> 01:47:48.629
See. that's being sensible again.

1444
01:47:48.630 --> 01:47:51.550
Can't be unhinged without
loosening the screws a bit every day.

1445
01:47:57.300 --> 01:48:00.339
And if you're still visiting your
partners' graves every month.

1446
01:48:00.340 --> 01:48:01.820
then yours are still pretty tight.

1447
01:48:03.100 --> 01:48:04.529
I'm heading home.

1448
01:48:04.530 --> 01:48:07.790
Aki's still a punk. so make
sure to work him over.

1449
01:48:08.410 --> 01:48:10.170
I'll take it one step at a time.

1450
01:48:10.860 --> 01:48:12.909
Not good enough.

1451
01:48:12.910 --> 01:48:16.669
The kid's serious about
collecting the meat chunks. right?

1452
01:48:16.670 --> 01:48:19.810
He's gonna actually find
the Gun Devil if he does.

1453
01:48:35.210 --> 01:48:36.200
No...

1454
01:48:36.480 --> 01:48:39.530
No. no. no. no. no. no—

1455
01:48:41.280 --> 01:48:42.540
No.

1456
01:48:43.130 --> 01:48:47.600
Aki. you wanna join
the private sector with me?

1457
01:48:48.460 --> 01:48:51.109
I received a pretty generous offer!

1458
01:48:51.110 --> 01:48:54.570
Being a private hunter means
you deal with less dangerous devils.

1459
01:48:54.960 --> 01:48:57.319
Instead of chasing the Gun.

1460
01:48:57.320 --> 01:49:01.810
we could go out for lunch.
see a movie on the way home.

1461
01:49:02.200 --> 01:49:04.190
and really enjoy ourselves.

1462
01:49:05.390 --> 01:49:07.939
If you wanna go out for drinks. I'll join you.

1463
01:49:07.940 --> 01:49:10.940
But I have no intention of ever going private.

1464
01:49:11.410 --> 01:49:13.200
And I'll take your almond tofu.

1465
01:49:14.470 --> 01:49:17.120
Then hand me a cigarette in exchange.

1466
01:49:24.420 --> 01:49:28.750
If Aki fights the Gun Devil. he's gonna die.

1467
01:49:29.660 --> 01:49:32.589
Not because we're too weak.

1468
01:49:32.590 --> 01:49:36.190
or because it's the kind of devil that
can kill hundreds of people in seconds.

1469
01:49:37.190 --> 01:49:42.120
It's because Aki's cool.
and serious. and kind...

1470
01:49:42.910 --> 01:49:45.240
and normal. like most people.

1471
01:49:46.510 --> 01:49:47.520
But...

1472
01:49:49.360 --> 01:49:50.860
Take that!

1473
01:49:52.090 --> 01:49:54.560
Ow. ow!

1474
01:49:59.120 --> 01:50:00.509
It...

1475
01:50:00.510 --> 01:50:02.130
It's over.

1476
01:50:06.800 --> 01:50:08.210
But him?

1477
01:50:08.880 --> 01:50:11.139
Eureka. dude.

1478
01:50:11.140 --> 01:50:14.479
I cut you up. and you bleed.

1479
01:50:14.480 --> 01:50:17.839
I drink that blood and heal!

1480
01:50:17.840 --> 01:50:22.010
I'm a fucking perpetual motion machine!

1481
01:50:22.880 --> 01:50:26.630
That Nobel Prize is mine!

1482
01:50:27.840 --> 01:50:30.850
I've never seen anyone crazier than him.

1483
01:50:31.330 --> 01:50:33.860
so maybe he can kill the Gun Devil!

1484
01:50:46.300 --> 01:50:48.060
Pain...

1485
01:50:53.130 --> 01:50:55.129
Ow. ow...

1486
01:50:55.130 --> 01:50:57.130
It hurts...

1487
01:51:00.270 --> 01:51:02.950
You still alive. Aki?

1488
01:51:05.890 --> 01:51:07.230
How long...

1489
01:51:07.850 --> 01:51:09.890
How long has it been?

1490
01:51:10.450 --> 01:51:14.020
About three days since
you got stabbed. I think?

1491
01:51:14.620 --> 01:51:16.270
Meowy...

1492
01:51:16.610 --> 01:51:19.800
Let's all go out for drinks.

1493
01:51:20.410 --> 01:51:24.030
Since it's over... I'm gonna sleep a bit.

1494
01:51:25.210 --> 01:51:26.680
It's over?

1495
01:51:28.620 --> 01:51:31.289
This is my weakness...

1496
01:51:31.290 --> 01:51:32.609
It's my heart.

1497
01:51:32.610 --> 01:51:34.309
Please kill me. I'm sorry.

1498
01:51:34.310 --> 01:51:35.119
I apologize.

1499
01:51:35.120 --> 01:51:36.420
It hurts...

1500
01:51:36.690 --> 01:51:38.969
What. already?!

1501
01:51:38.970 --> 01:51:43.430
I was still having fun!
It was like being in a pool!

1502
01:51:51.040 --> 01:51:52.560
We're out.

1503
01:51:55.700 --> 01:51:59.609
Got a piece of the Gun Devil's flesh.
the sky is clear...

1504
01:51:59.610 --> 01:52:02.080
And I'm feeling good.
like I just took a huge shit.

1505
01:52:02.450 --> 01:52:04.750
It's like I'm floating...

1506
01:52:06.630 --> 01:52:07.650
Whoa there.

1507
01:52:09.440 --> 01:52:10.750
He's out...

1508
01:52:11.450 --> 01:52:14.500
Makes sense. considering he was fighting
the devil the whole time without sleeping.

1509
01:52:16.320 --> 01:52:19.750
We'll get Aki and Denji to a hospital.

1510
01:52:20.090 --> 01:52:23.280
You two head back to the office and check in.

1511
01:52:30.840 --> 01:52:32.769
A welcoming party?

1512
01:52:32.770 --> 01:52:33.789
Yep.

1513
01:52:33.790 --> 01:52:36.639
Since the full Division 4
is finally assembled.

1514
01:52:36.640 --> 01:52:38.409
we ought to get to know each other better.

1515
01:52:38.410 --> 01:52:41.549
and deal with some of our outstanding issues.

1516
01:52:41.550 --> 01:52:42.689
What issues?

1517
01:52:42.690 --> 01:52:48.119
Well. the thing is. Kobeni and Arai
are talking about quitting Public Safety.

1518
01:52:48.120 --> 01:52:51.270
I guess that thing with that last devil
traumatized them a bit.

1519
01:52:51.910 --> 01:52:54.639
Not only are they afraid of the devils.

1520
01:52:54.640 --> 01:52:57.420
they feel pretty guilty
about trying to kill Denji. too.

1521
01:52:58.240 --> 01:53:00.799
You tried to kill him. too.

1522
01:53:00.800 --> 01:53:02.019
I know. right?!

1523
01:53:02.020 --> 01:53:05.299
Kids these days! They're so sensitive.

1524
01:53:05.300 --> 01:53:08.300
Would it kill them to be a little bolder?

1525
01:53:09.040 --> 01:53:12.439
Over drinks. they'll be able to
apologize to Denji easily.

1526
01:53:12.440 --> 01:53:14.729
and we'll be able to
convince them to not quit.

1527
01:53:14.730 --> 01:53:16.350
You're just in this for drinks.

1528
01:53:18.560 --> 01:53:20.920
It wasn't much. but I found
a chunk of its flesh.

1529
01:53:21.710 --> 01:53:24.249
If we're doing this.
it needs to be this week.

1530
01:53:24.250 --> 01:53:25.949
Why's that?

1531
01:53:25.950 --> 01:53:29.280
If we're having a drinking party.
I want to invite Ms. Makima.

1532
01:53:36.340 --> 01:53:39.059
She's going on a business trip
to Kyoto next week.

1533
01:53:39.060 --> 01:53:43.249
With so many devils targeting Denji.
she's looking into getting reinforcements.

1534
01:53:43.250 --> 01:53:45.450
So the party needs to be this week.

1535
01:53:48.350 --> 01:53:49.760
Be honest with me.

1536
01:53:50.080 --> 01:53:52.380
What do you think Denji is?

1537
01:53:54.140 --> 01:53:57.749
That devil seemed to know about him.

1538
01:53:57.750 --> 01:53:59.899
and I've never seen anything
like what he turned into.

1539
01:53:59.900 --> 01:54:04.650
But the biggest mystery is how much
Ms. Makima seems to be interested in him.

1540
01:54:06.400 --> 01:54:10.479
She used to travel all the time.
but she's stuck to Tokyo lately.

1541
01:54:10.480 --> 01:54:12.470
and that's probably because of Denji.

1542
01:54:13.050 --> 01:54:16.040
Does she know his secret?

1543
01:54:20.090 --> 01:54:22.920
Wanna get her hammered and ask about it?

1544
01:55:56.240 --> 01:55:58.320
Chainsaw Days.

1545
01:56:00.460 --> 01:56:02.690
What a waste.

1546
01:56:07.850 --> 01:56:09.939
Dude. don't toss the apple skins.

1547
01:56:09.940 --> 01:56:11.800
They're edible.

1548
01:56:16.650 --> 01:56:19.079
If you're not gonna eat
the orange skin. gimme.

1549
01:56:19.080 --> 01:56:20.380
I'll eat it.

1550
01:56:25.240 --> 01:56:27.079
Gimme the scab.

1551
01:56:27.080 --> 01:56:28.620
I'll eat it.

1552
01:56:30.120 --> 01:56:31.839
Not this time.

1553
01:56:31.840 --> 01:56:34.180
Why the hell not?! It's nutritious!

1554
01:56:34.530 --> 01:56:37.090
What kind of life have you lived?

1555
01:56:39.520 --> 01:56:42.480
Denji and My Staple Recipe.

1556
01:56:42.850 --> 01:56:45.840
(Flour)
Step 1: Buy some flour.

1557
01:56:52.860 --> 01:56:56.380
Step 2: Take some water
and mix it into the flour.

1558
01:57:05.280 --> 01:57:08.390
Step 3: Eat it (soup style).

1559
01:57:09.960 --> 01:57:11.760
But today...

1560
01:57:16.490 --> 01:57:19.040
Because it's Christmas...

1561
01:57:29.120 --> 01:57:30.690
Complete!

1562
01:57:31.650 --> 01:57:37.129
Step 4: Because it's Christmas. add
some sugar before eating (soup style).

1563
01:57:37.130 --> 01:57:40.640
So good! Tastes just like cake!

1564
01:57:43.200 --> 01:57:46.560
Neither of us have had cake before.

1565
01:57:50.000 --> 01:57:51.960
A mature flavor.

1566
01:57:53.230 --> 01:57:55.170
The coffee here is good.

1567
01:57:58.110 --> 01:58:00.110
Never had coffee before!

1568
01:58:01.430 --> 01:58:03.560
Dude. this is muddy water!

1569
01:58:04.260 --> 01:58:08.010
How pitiful.
A taste too sophisticated for a child.

1570
01:58:09.640 --> 01:58:10.920
Sludge!

1571
01:58:13.300 --> 01:58:15.469
My tongue is tingling!

1572
01:58:15.470 --> 01:58:17.029
What the fuck. dude?!

1573
01:58:17.030 --> 01:58:19.519
Shut up!
We're in a restaurant. keep it down!

1574
01:58:19.520 --> 01:58:22.089
What kinda sick joke is this?!

1575
01:58:22.090 --> 01:58:23.199
That was mud!

1576
01:58:23.200 --> 01:58:24.960
Some sort of mud beverage!

1577
01:58:27.110 --> 01:58:28.670
Topknot.

1578
01:58:30.360 --> 01:58:34.340
So. is there a reason for the weird hairstyle?

1579
01:58:34.650 --> 01:58:39.089
My deal with the Fox means she makes
requests other than skin. sometimes.

1580
01:58:39.090 --> 01:58:42.110
And when I give her the topknot.
she seems to enjoy it.

1581
01:58:44.030 --> 01:58:47.609
Sounds good to me! I want one. too!

1582
01:58:47.610 --> 01:58:48.609
No.

1583
01:58:48.610 --> 01:58:50.160
Cheapskate.

1584
01:58:52.720 --> 01:58:55.110
We have drinks at her place
about once a week.

1585
01:59:13.900 --> 01:59:16.159
That was drunk me that did it!

1586
01:59:16.160 --> 01:59:18.649
So. sober me is asking for lenience.

1587
01:59:18.650 --> 01:59:21.209
Come on. please. Aki?

1588
01:59:21.210 --> 01:59:23.329
I kind of have to forgive her. Because...

1589
01:59:23.330 --> 01:59:24.669
I'm sorry.

1590
01:59:24.670 --> 01:59:27.250
she has way too much dirt
she could use against me.

1591
01:59:27.850 --> 01:59:29.420
I'm making it into a family treasure!

1592
01:59:30.305 --> 02:00:30.750
